\id JHN - Sembeleke 2 Samberigi PNG John 01 23/2/91 Macnaughtan 
\h DIONI 
\toc1 Dionimaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe 
\toc2 Dioni 
\toc3 Dioni 
\mt1 Dionimaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe  
\c 1  
\s1 Deto halaęž‰ Pi  
\p
\v 1 Ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ do kenke ya yaapo aĚ±iĚ± na wepia winaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Pitaęž‰ hao hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo hao hayekepate Kodaęž‰ hayeke tupaęž‰ kone ipiki make hayekeme.  
\v 2 Ipikitaęž‰ mo kini pieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰ yaapo mandakenaęž‰ hao hayekeme.  
\v 3 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ leeke handaataęž‰ mo hande Pimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao wepia winaęž‰ leekepate aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰siki kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honumake hataęž‰ na wepia winaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 4 Mo hande Pi paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki pitiekeme. Kutupa mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki pitiekeme.  
\v 5 Mo hande paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo timbaęž‰ laęž‰pa pulaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰pate kone mo hande timbaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki na honiao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi mea epenaęž‰ tapaeyeke halitaęž‰ Dioni tapaeyekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali waluekemaęž‰ epeekeme. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea epeeke pi opua pi minaęž‰yeke handa loluekemaęž‰ epeekeme.  
\v 8 Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande paĚ±aĚ± na peaeyekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ waluekemaęž‰ epeekeme.  
\v 9 Mo hande paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki yaalo hataęž‰ kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa mo hande Pitaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ aęž‰pa hayekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ leeke handa alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ leekepate kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hone na wimikime.  
\v 11 Ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kenke teke nane epeekepate kone ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki na handaęž‰ mimikime.  
\v 12 Kutu pimikipate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki handaęž‰ meataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hatiki pimikime. Kutu pimiki handaataęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ weki wandiki haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki wandiki haenaęž‰ leekepate kenke halimaęž‰ mendiaasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ na mendiaeyekeme. Kodaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ hayekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Mo hande Pitaęž‰ hali au la aęž‰pa niki ameĚ±leĚ± hayaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pu halaęž‰eki pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make tumba pitiaęž‰eki nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handomaęž‰me. Koto hande paĚ±aĚ± pu halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Atekenaęž‰ Eiyeke homeke kone hataęž‰ miekeme.   
\p
\v 15 Dionimaęž‰ Yesu halaęž‰eki niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuluekemaęž‰ wi la alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande lo haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Ya hoki nane ipilie halitaęž‰ IĚ± na mendiki haenaęž‰ kone ipiki ambaęž‰la hao hayeke ekimaęž‰ IĚ± ankulalaęž‰me. Kutupa hande lo haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ do hali paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 16 Ipikaęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki tumba halaęž‰eki mea niki kiaęž‰tiki kiaęž‰tiki peaataęž‰ niki paeyao ambaęž‰ epeaalaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kinaęž‰yeke Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme. Kutu piekepate pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ mea aęž‰paeyekeme.  
\v 18 Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ otaęž‰ na handeekeme. Kutu piekepate Eiyeke homekemaęž‰ homeke Kodaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ Atekenaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pilaęž‰ halimaęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki la kaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dioninaęž‰ pi  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 3ęž‰1-12, Maka 1ęž‰1-18, Luku 3ęž‰1-18)  
\p
\v 19 Dionimaęž‰ koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme nane haemeke Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ yeni peao haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Lipae tapake haliwekimaęž‰ make Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ Neketaęž‰ epikaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pulu penaęž‰ tapaemekeme.  
\v 20 Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ Ikaęž‰ pi IĚ±maęž‰ na hombo peaalueke pi na leke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ bao alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketiso diaęž‰me la leekeme.  
\v 21 Koto leeke mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Neketaęž‰ Elaidiape lemekeme. Dionimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ koto hali diaęž‰me leekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo hande Potopede halipe lemekeme. Dionimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ koto hali diaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 22 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke haleeki niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kie laataęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ opua niki tapaeme haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lolo pomonoyeke neke haleeki kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ eki pi lelipikipe lemekeme.  
\v 23 Dionimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± halo ekitaęž‰ dupae. Hali homekemaęž‰ mo hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ wi alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Tekehali epenaęž‰yeke potaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ pilaapaęž‰peke. Koto leeke pitaęž‰ mo potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ wape pieke pi kone leekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Mo lotaęž‰ pulu penaęž‰ tapaemeke haliwekitaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ tapaemekeme.  
\v 25 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Dioni lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Ketiso make Elaidia make mo hande Potopede hali make na hataęž‰ kone ekipeke wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peao halepe lemekeme.  
\v 26 Dionimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ikalimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaaso halopate iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handelememe.  
\v 27 Koto halitaęž‰ ya hoki nane ipulaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ anke dake limbiti paęž‰laęž‰ pu IĚ±maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰papeke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 28 Koto hau pimiki ekitaęž‰ mo Bedani da paęž‰taęž‰ mo Diodani ikali mone teaęž‰naęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peaeyeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pimikime.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki  
\p
\v 29 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu epeekeeki handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰siki koto ipulaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰pe laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu mea pulaęž‰me.  
\v 30 Hande loaęž‰ ale hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaka hoki nane ipiliepate IĚ± na mendiki haenaęž‰ kone ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hao hayeke ekimaęž‰ IĚ± ankulalaęž‰me loaęž‰me laataęž‰  
\v 31 Hande halitaęž‰ epipe laa hone na uaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ waluekemaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peaalo epoaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 32 Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ pi la halolo hataęž‰ dupiki pi leekeme. Hande melipumaęž‰ handeke ba aĚ±iĚ±ya holaęž‰paęž‰niaasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo Sipitiditaęž‰ hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰pa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitiaęž‰eki IĚ±maęž‰ handoaęž‰me laa  
\v 33 Koto pitaęž‰ kone IĚ±maęž‰ mo hali epipe hone na uaęž‰pate hande ikalimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peaalo pono IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Holi Sipitiditaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰eki handilipikie laa koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peao halaęž‰me leaęž‰me laa leekeme.  
\v 34 Dionimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handoaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke halaęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolome leekeme.   
\s1 Ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki  
\p
\v 35 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ Dioni make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo make koto paęž‰taęž‰ paa aęž‰pa hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 36 Yesu yapeekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰sikie leekeme.  
\v 37 Mo hande disaipolo hali yaapomaęž‰ koto leeke pi opuaataęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 38 Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina ipiki teliaęž‰ mea epepekeeki handaa ipiliki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Aleke weitelepepe leekeme. Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Laęž‰baio. Neketaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ hao halepe lepekeme. Do Laęž‰bai alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Disa la kone alaęž‰ekie.  
\v 39 Yesumaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aęž‰pa handaęž‰pe la leeke handaa ipikaęž‰ hayeke alenaęž‰ handolo puaataęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± hao haemekeme. Koto hau pimiki hautaęž‰ welealo nane 4 okoloko pimikime.   
\p
\v 40 Mo hande hali yaapotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ leeke pi opua Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± halo pepeke hali yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰ndutue. Saimono Pida ipikaęž‰ hamekee.  
\v 41 Koto kone Aęž‰ndutumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke Saimono handaęž‰ wia ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande Mesayataęž‰ dikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ ulupaęž‰me leekeme. Do Mesaya alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Ketisoe laa alaęž‰ekie.  
\v 42 Koto pi laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ Saimono hatuku peekeme. Yesumaęž‰ Saimono handolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ eiyeke Saimonoe. Wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki Sipasi lelimikie. Koto bikitaęž‰ Pida kone homeke niki Toopi la kone leekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Pilipi Nadaęž‰niele yaapo wi leekeeki  
\p
\v 43 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane polueke hone wiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pilipi handaęž‰ wia ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dikaęž‰ panaęž‰ epoe leekeme.  
\v 44 Pilipitaęž‰ Betesaida halie. Hande Aęž‰ndutu Pida yaapo haepeke da konee.  
\v 45 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pilipimaęž‰ Nadaęž‰niele handaęž‰ wia ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande Mosesimaęž‰ Lo Pimanu wape pitolo hataęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ hali kone handaęž‰ ulumaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Diosepenaęž‰ eiyeke Yesue laa leekeme.  
\v 46 Naęž‰saęž‰tete nanemaęž‰ epekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipulaęž‰eki handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Pilipimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰pa handaęž‰taa leekeme.   
\p
\v 47 Nadaęž‰niele Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu haenaęž‰ kone Yesumaęž‰ handa Nadaęž‰nielenaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae laa maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Isulai halie laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 48 Nadaęž‰nielemaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ekipa handa alepe leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Pilipimaęž‰ neke wi aĚ±iĚ± na leeke dinaęž‰ kone neketaęž‰ mo hande nose ti teke paęž‰taęž‰ pitieki IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ handoaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 49 Nadaęž‰nielemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Disao. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee. Neketaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie leekeme.  
\v 50 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neketaęž‰ nose ti teke paęž‰taęž‰ pitieki handoaęž‰me loaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone tulaaso alepe laa kutupiki hausunu ankulalo peleme hau tieke tiekemanu pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki handilipikie leekeme.  
\v 51 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikitaęž‰ hepeni nane lombaęž‰pa ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo haliweki mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niatiki aęž‰meiyatiki pilimieki handilimikie leekeme.   
\c 2  
\s1 Keina da paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ miekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Nate yaapo paeyeketaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke da Keina da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ wandaęž‰ miekeme. Kutupa Yesunaęž‰ inkiki make koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.  
\v 2 Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ hapieke alenaęž‰ ipupe laa wi leekeme.  
\v 3 Mo hande waini ikali no paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pitieketaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ inkikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande waini ikali no paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pilaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 4 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Ya pulu poloeki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ dupi dupi laa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na lelipikie laataęž‰ Ya natetaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na ipulaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 5 Pate ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰lie pi opua peaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hande ikalimaęž‰ tandepaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu haemeke ekinaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ wepia ikali kanake yunki mindiki hataęž‰ mo paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeme. Kanake homeke paęž‰taęž‰ ikalitaęž‰ 80 lida o 90 lida tupaęž‰ pitaapeke yeekeme.  
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ mo e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo toopi ikali kanake manunaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ tumba tumba pipe leekeme. Koto leeke mo haliwekimaęž‰ mo ipi kanakemanu tumba tumba pimikime.  
\v 8 Kutu pu paeyeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mandane ekitaęž‰ kanake mandane ekinaęž‰ yupu tia mo ne handeteke halaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua halaęž‰pe leekeme. Koto leeke mo ikali mandaneeki yupa mea pua halemekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ mea naa handeekepate otaęž‰ waini ikalimaęž‰ kone handeekeme. Mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ koto waini ikali yupimikieki paęž‰taęž‰ hone na wiekepate hande ikali yupimiki e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ hone wimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ tekehali wi laęž‰ mea  
\v 10 ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ waini ikali otaęž‰ epekeeki ambaęž‰la hale hale pea kutupa mo ne nolo epo laa epemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ waini ikali wopu nemeke hoki nanetaęž‰ mo hosiki metoko piki waini ikali hale hale pilieke. Pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo otaęž‰ epeke waini ikalitaęž‰ hosiki saęž‰saęž‰ pea wia hao ame kone hale hale pinaęž‰ aleme leekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke da Keina da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele piekeeki koto paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la piekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kapu tieke halaęž‰eki peneme yao waleeke handaa ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.   
\p
\v 12 Kutu pieke hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesu make ipikaęž‰ inkiki make ipikaęž‰ hameketiti make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ paeyao Kapeneami da paęž‰taęž‰ pua hoto mandane ekimanu koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.   
\s1 Yesu mo tembolo da nane peekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰12-13, Maka 11ęž‰15-17, Luku 19ęž‰45-46)  
\p
\v 13 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ haemeke handaataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da nane peekeme.  
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua handeekepate mandane haliwekimaęž‰ kao make sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu make melipumaęž‰ handeke bamanu make mandane haliwekimaęž‰ hambenaęž‰yeke wia pitimikieki make mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ teipolo paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ mani topo pimikieki make handeekeme.  
\v 15 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pu tunkulikimanu meaataęž‰ ponkaęž‰ pilimepi pea depita wepiaataęž‰ paeyao hama penaęž‰ mo kao sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ tolu liekeme. Mo mani topo pu pitimiki haliwekinaęž‰ teipolomanu londolo ba ba pea ikaęž‰ manimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hoelo ba ba piekeme.  
\v 16 Kutupa mo melipumaęž‰ handeke bamanu wia pitimiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do alemanu mu tia hama pupe. Yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ dataęž‰ makedi da au na lapaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 17 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki hone wimikime dupae. Kodaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ da epeaalo polo hone witolo ekitaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ titipu wopu polome wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 18 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaluekemaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do pitele hautaęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰eki niki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ waluekemaęž‰ eki wele piteleeki pilipiki lemekeme.  
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da leisimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hoto teponaęž‰ pa mea aęž‰meiyao haenaęž‰ lolueke leekeme.  
\v 20 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hande tembolo da aęž‰etolo haenaęž‰ 46 bapimanu ambaęž‰ paeyaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoto teponaęž‰ kone paa mea aęž‰meiyao haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ alepe lemekeme.  
\v 21 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo hande tembolo da leeke ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ kone leekeme.  
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesu homeeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa mea tiaeyeke natenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ do leeke pi hone wimikime. Kutupa mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki make Yesumaęž‰ leeke pimanu make hone tulaemekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ haliweki paeyaonaęž‰ honetaęž‰ handeekeeki  
\p
\v 23 Mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ne pambemeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wele wotu pieke ekimanu wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekepate  
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ikaęž‰ piteleme ekimanu wotu handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaaso hataęž‰ na taleekeme.  
\v 25 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekimanu Yesumaęž‰ wotu handeeke ekinaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰peke na yeekeme.   
\c 3  
\s1 Yesu Nikodimasi yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Handa Paęž‰tisi tapake hali homeke Nikodimasitaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ KaĚ±leĚ±sete hali hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 2 nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ timba Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Disao. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tapaaleke walele hali hale ekitaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wele pitele tupaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo na hake halimaęž‰ wele peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me la leekeme.  
\v 3 Koto pi leeke handa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ pa panake weki leke na mendiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki na handilieke leekeme.  
\v 4 Nikodimasimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Keileke halimaęž‰taęž‰ ekipa panake weki leke paa mendiliekepe laa Ipikaęž‰ inkikimaęž‰ hoto yaapo peao paa mendinaęž‰ alepe leekeme.  
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ make Sipitidimaęž‰ make ipikitaęž‰ panake weki leke paa na mendiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na hondaęž‰ pamba pelieke laa  
\v 6 weki mondu halaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke halaęž‰eki kone mondu halaęž‰pate mo Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikimaęž‰ handekeeki kone pitaalieke laa leekeme.  
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paeyao pa panake weki wandiki leke mendia haminaęž‰ alo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hone taęž‰taęž‰ na wiaęž‰peke.  
\v 8 Po ipulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone ipulaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ u la ipulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ opitelepate hao ipulaęž‰eki make mandane pulaęž‰eki make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na handilipikie. Kutupa mo pomaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make panake weki leke mendilieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 9 Kotoeki opua Nikodimasimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ale ekitaęž‰ ekipa peaaliepe leekeme.  
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ do Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ hali tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ halepate do aloeki manutaęž‰ hone na wiaalepe.  
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome laa Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ honemaęž‰ handolomaęž‰ ekimanu make lekemaęž‰ handolomaęž‰ ekimanu make la kitolomaęž‰pate iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make do pi opuluekemaęž‰ hone na witaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Do kenkenaęž‰eki IĚ±maęž‰ walolo ekimanu na opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ oli hepeni nane pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu waloaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make ekipa opilimikipe.  
\v 13 Kutupa hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ oli hepeni nane na paęž‰laęž‰pate hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke hepeni nane hao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ hali homekee laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Hande Mosesimaęž‰ mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ mo keto mea aęž‰meiyaeyeke tupaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰  
\v 15 ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki minaęž‰yeke haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki mea aęž‰meiyalieke.  
\v 16 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wotu homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Weki homeke kone kiekeme. Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Weki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hali na homeke deto halaęž‰eki minaęž‰yeke kiekeme.  
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Weki kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaalo paęž‰laęž‰ hali haenaęž‰yeke na tapake ikaęž‰ mea daęž‰taalo paęž‰laęž‰ hali haenaęž‰yeke tapaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ mo hande Weki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu pilieeki paęž‰taęž‰ na pelieke. Pate hali epimaęž‰ hone na tulao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande pi yokaalu pilie natenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Weki homeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulao hayeke ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wini peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 19 Mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Do kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki ambaęž‰ epaęž‰laęž‰pate haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu pu haleme ekinaęž‰ hande paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kiao mo timbaęž‰laęž‰ pambaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ hone witelememe.  
\v 20 Hoke hau pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu peneme yao walaapaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ kiaaso hataęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na ipilimikie.  
\v 21 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pu halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke. Kutupa mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ piekeeki manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo hataęž‰ pieke ekimanu peneme yao walenaęž‰yeke ipilieke.   
\s1 Yesu Dioni yaapo  
\p
\v 22 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo Diudia nane pua koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peatiki pimikime.  
\v 23 Dionimaęž‰ make mo Seilimi da teke paęž‰taęž‰ Inoni da hataęž‰taęž‰ ikali wotu pitieke handaa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰tiki pimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ bapitaisi peatiki piekeme.  
\v 24 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ Dioni dipula aĚ±iĚ± na pitaake haenaęž‰ piekeme.   
\p
\v 25 Kutupa Dioninaęž‰ disaipolo mandane haliwekimaęž‰ mo Diu hali homeke ameĚ±leĚ± mo pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ peiyaęž‰tiki piaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pimikime.  
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Disao. Mo Diodani ikali mone tenaęž‰ neke yaapo mandakenaęž‰ hayaęž‰ halitaęž‰ hande nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ bapitaisi peaaseke handaa wandaęž‰hali wopu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pitelememe lemekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa  
\v 28 IĚ±taęž‰ Ketiso diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ titinaęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰la tapaalaęž‰me laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opimime leekeme. Hande wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ halikinaęž‰eki halieke laa  
\v 29 mo wandaęž‰ teke halinaęž‰ hameketaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ hataęž‰ kone wandaęž‰ teke halimaęž‰ lelie pi opitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ tumba ulaęž‰me laa  
\v 30 Ipikitaęž‰ tieke daeyatiki pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hosiki uniatiki peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Oli manda hao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ hali  
\p
\v 31 Oli manda hao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ manda halieke. Kenkenaęž‰ hao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ kenke pimanu lelieke. Oli manda hepeni nane hao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao manda hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 32 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰eki make opitaęž‰laęž‰eki make la kitaęž‰laęž‰pate wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opua na miniki halememe.  
\v 33 Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opua miniki hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰eki alaęž‰me laa lelieke.  
\v 34 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu lalieke. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Holi Sipitidi halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ tombo wia na halaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 35 Atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao Eiyekenaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 36 Hali epimaęž‰ hande Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰ hao halo paęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ hande Eiyekenaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ na homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki na miki haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki koto hali paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me.   
\c 4  
\s1 Yesu mo hande Sametia wandaęž‰ yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Paęž‰tisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa laęž‰niaeyekeme. Yesumaęž‰ disaipolo wandaęž‰hali wopu meaataęž‰ bapitaisi peao pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wetepe yaasaęž‰me laa laęž‰niaeyekeme.  
\v 2 Koto laęž‰niaeyekepate Yesu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ bapitaisi na peaake ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ homeke bapitaisi peatiki pimikime.  
\v 3 Koto laęž‰niaeyeke pitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ make opuaataęž‰ mo hande Diudia nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Kaęž‰lili nane peekeme.   
\p
\v 4 Koto nane pulu hataęž‰ Sametia nanemaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰ peekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa Sametia lopaęž‰laęž‰ puaataęž‰ daoni homeke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme. Koto daoni bikitaęž‰ Saika lemekeme. Mo da teketaęž‰ hande Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ haleeke kenke teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke dae.  
\v 6 Koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ aweeke naku paęž‰taęž‰ ikali pitiekeme. Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ ipu hao anke litu pieke mo naku ikali teke paęž‰taęž‰ pitiekeme. Nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ pitiekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Kutupa pitinaęž‰ Sametia wandaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ ikali nolo epeekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ nono kie leekeme.  
\v 8 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ ne hambolo penaęž‰ pitaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 9 Mo Sametia wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Sametia wandaęž‰ halopate neketaęž‰ Diu hali hataęž‰ kone ekipeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ Ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ nono kie laa honke alepe leekeme. Koto Sametia wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne ikali no haemeke kawaso manutaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yolaęž‰ alu pea napeke na yeeke handa loaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ale make neke paęž‰taęž‰ Ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ nono kie laa honke alaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki make hone wikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ honke aleeki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ opua daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ikali kulu piaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Do nakutaęž‰ otaęž‰ oni paęž‰taęž‰ leke awaęž‰niaalaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ neketaęž‰ ipi kanake na wia halepate daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ikali ekipa naa kuluekemaęž‰ alepe laataęž‰  
\v 12 Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ do naku ikali niki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me. Do ikalitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ eiyeke titimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ make naęž‰tiki pu haemekeme. Neketaęž‰ Dieikope ankulaluekemaęž‰ alepe leekeme.  
\v 13 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ do naku ikali naa haotaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ make ikali nenaęž‰ pa peaęž‰tiki pilieke.  
\v 14 Kutu piliepate hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ halolo ikali naa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ ikali nenaęž‰ paa na pilieke. IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ halolo ikalitaęž‰ mo hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ ikali kone pitilieke. Kutupa hande ikalimaęž‰taęž‰ opolo hataęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ daęž‰tao haenaęž‰ lelieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 15 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ale ikalitaęž‰ IĚ± maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie leekeme. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ ikali nenaęž‰ paa na pitolo hataęž‰ do naku ikali nolo paa na ipulueke leekeme.  
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ haliki ambaęž‰la wi lolo puaataęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ paa aęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 17 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hali diaęž‰me leekeme.  
\p Koto leeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hali diaęž‰me ale ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi aleme.  
\v 18 Neketaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ da ambaęž‰ pekepate ame do halepe hali make otaęž‰ nakaęž‰ haliki diaęž‰me laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ale ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ekie leekeme.  
\v 19 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Ametaęž‰ neke handolome laa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halo hale hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 20 Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰ niki Sametia wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Do pote paęž‰taęž‰ pua mombela Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰paęž‰peke laa lemekepate Diu haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ pua mombela Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰paęž‰peke alememe leekeme.   
\p
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. IĚ±maęž‰ do aloeki opuaęž‰peke. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipilieke laa koto nate epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do pote paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ make oli Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hande Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni na pilimikie laataęž‰  
\v 22 Iki Sametia wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni piteleme ekitaęž‰ epi paęž‰taęž‰ pitelemepe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wopu na handelememe. Kutu pitelemepate niki Diu wandaęž‰hali nikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni pitolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epi paęž‰taęž‰ pitolomaęž‰pe kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kini pea ipulaęž‰eke handa loaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 23 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate wetepe hande epolo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ ame ambaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ yeni piteleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ temokomaęž‰ make otaęž‰ hau pitolo hataęž‰ make yeni pilimikie leekeme. Koto tupaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piteleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 24 Kodaęž‰taęž‰ temoko tekee. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piteleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ temokomaęž‰ make otaęž‰ hau pitolo hataęž‰ make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 25 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Mesaya ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki hone witolome. Ipiki aęž‰paataęž‰ hau paeyao pitaęž‰laęž‰eki la kilieke leekeme.  
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ale halitaęž‰ IĚ± konee laataęž‰ Neke yaapo do pi alopaęž‰ halie leekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Koto pi alo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paa opolo epemekepate Yesu mo wandaęž‰ yaapo pi alo haepekeeki handaataęž‰ hone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ wimikipate hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Aleke muluekemaęž‰ alepe o Ipiki yaapo ekipeke pi alepe laa pa na lotaęž‰ piekeme.   
\p
\v 28 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipi kanake minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo daoni nane puaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 29 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ handoemenaęž‰ ipupe laataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ puaęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ la kiaęž‰me laataęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ hande Ketisope leekeme.  
\v 30 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ daoni minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesu handolo pemekeme.   
\p
\v 31 Koto hau pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ hande disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu honke alo alotaęž‰ Disao. Ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ nae lemekepate  
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ya netaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ulaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handeleme leekeme.  
\v 33 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ane laęž‰ mone laęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ne mea aęž‰pao haleaęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka netaęž‰ dupae. IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ halinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰ e make pokao paeyawaaluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 35 Kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ aleme pitaęž‰ dupae. Sumbaęž‰ tonkopu yapeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ne napeke naa pilie natenaęž‰ pokaęž‰ mepi pilimikie lo halemepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Emanu lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ame kone ne napeketaęž‰ naa paęž‰leke handaa pokaęž‰ mepi piaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 36 Ne napeke pokaęž‰ mepi pitaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yenki minolo hataęž‰ mo hande ne napekemanu mea pua mombaęž‰la wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰eki kone yelieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ne wae nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ hali make napeke pokaęž‰ mepi pitaęž‰laęž‰ hali make ipiliki telipinaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilipipikie leekeme.  
\v 37 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo hande lo halomaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa yaasaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ne wae nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ne napeke pokaęž‰ mepi pitaęž‰laęž‰me alomaęž‰me laataęž‰  
\v 38 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na pokeme e paęž‰taęž‰ kone ne napekemanu pokaęž‰ mepi puemenaęž‰yeke iki tapaalome. Kutupa mandane haliwekimaęž‰ pokeme e paęž‰taęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ne napeke pokaęž‰ mepi pulu pelemepatetaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ honkopu hao pu wilimi haunaęž‰ pitelememe leekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Mo hande wandaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ la kiaęž‰me leeke ekinaęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke Sametia wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.  
\v 40 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande Sametia wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ Niki ameĚ±leĚ± hosiki hao polenaęž‰e laa honke lemekeme. Koto lemeke handa hoto yaapo Yesu koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.   
\p
\v 41 Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ waleeke pi opitolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 42 Ametaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ lele ekinaęž‰ hone na tulaake nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ pi opuaataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali hande mea Daęž‰taasaęž‰ Hali otaęž‰ halaęž‰me hone witolomaęž‰me lemekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo kapomani halinaęž‰ eiyeke mea tiaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 43 Yesutaęž‰ hoto yaapo koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao pa Kaęž‰lili nane peekeme.  
\v 44 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone leekeme dupae. Potopede halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ da teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki na wilieke leekeme.  
\v 45 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane opolo peeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki handaęž‰ mimikime. Do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ kone Diutuseleme nane puaataęž‰ hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ ne nalo hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke haumanu paeyao ambaęž‰ handemekeme.   
\p
\v 46 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke da Keina paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme. Ambaęž‰taęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ otaęž‰ ikali kone waini ikali pitinaęž‰ leekeme. Koto da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kapomani hali homeke hayekepate ipikaęž‰ wekitaęž‰ Kapeneami da paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hayekeme.  
\v 47 Koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Diudia nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao Kaęž‰lili nane aęž‰pa halaęž‰me leekeeki opuaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo Kapeneami nane pua ipikaęž‰ homoluekemaęž‰ taapo pitieke weki mea tiaenaęž‰yeke honke leekeme.  
\v 48 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hau tieke ipulaęž‰eki handolo homeke pa hone tulaasememe leekeme.   
\p
\v 49 Mo hande kapomani halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Yaka weki homaapaęž‰naęž‰ dikaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ panaęž‰e laa leekeme.  
\v 50 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ weki tiaaliekemaęž‰ pue leekeme. Hande halimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke pi opua hone tulao hao peekeme.  
\v 51 Mo ipikaęž‰ da nane paa poluekemaęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ mandaęž‰hande pea alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ weki tiao pilaęž‰me lemekeme.   
\p
\v 52 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ya weki hosiki tiaeyeke hautaęž‰ nate hando paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ piekepe laa lotaęž‰ pieke handaa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ambaneke nate lekelo yopulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoputiti yenitaęž‰ tandeleaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 53 Atekemaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Ambaneke koto natenaęž‰ kone Yesumaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ weki tiaalieke laa leaęž‰me hone wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰maęž‰ make hone tulaemekeme.   
\p
\v 54 Yesutaęž‰ Diudia nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao Kaęž‰lili nane pua hayeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ do wele wopu pieke ekitaęž‰ hoto yaapo peaoeki piekeme.   
\c 5  
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Bedeseda ikali paęž‰taęž‰ hali mea tiaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Koto hau piekeeki hoki nanetaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ ne mieke nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu make Diutuseleme nane peekeme.  
\v 2 Mo Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hande Sipisipi Potaęž‰ Kake nepoko paęž‰taęž‰ tunkulaęž‰pa pilaęž‰ ikali kendo ulaęž‰me. Hibulu pi laa mo ikali bikitaęž‰ Bedeseda lo halememe. Koto ikali nepoko paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ tu peaasaęž‰ da yunki hataęž‰ halaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Koto dasunu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ yeni haemeke wandaęž‰hali wopu haemekeme. Leke holupiki wandaęž‰hali make anke hoke wandaęž‰hali make kiki anke tindipa tindipa peaęž‰peke na yeke wandaęž‰hali make koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ikalitaęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ pinaęž‰yeke handeteke hatiki pimikime.  
\v 4 Do ekinaęž‰yeke pimikime. Hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolo halimaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰pa mo hande ikali tapaęž‰tiaeyekeme. Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la hondaęž‰ pambiliaęž‰ halinaęž‰ yenitaęž‰ tandelelieke.  
\v 5 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni hayeke bapitaęž‰ 38 bapimanu ambaęž‰ yapeekeme.  
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ mo hali pelia hake wiekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni hapa winaęž‰ bapi wopu yapeekeeki make hone wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yeni tandelenaęž‰ hone witelepe leekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Mo yeni hapa wieke halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Mo ikali tapaęž‰tiatia pitaęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ IĚ± mea miniliao ikali paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku puaęž‰peke hali diaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ya kone pu pituaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± wetepeao yapilieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiao nakaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ mea mina anke lopao pue leekeme.  
\v 9 Kotaęž‰ koto kone mo hande halitaęž‰ epeke loke haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ mea mina anke lopao peekeme.  
\p Koto hau pieke ekitaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ pieke handaa  
\v 10 mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ koto yeni tandelaeyeke hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ mea mina puli ekitaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambololo piteleme lemekeme.  
\v 11 Kotaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ya yeni tandelaeyaęž‰ halimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ mea mina anke lopao puaęž‰peke leaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 12 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neke paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ yapaęž‰taęž‰ mea mina puaęž‰peke leaęž‰ halitaęž‰ epipe lemekepate  
\v 13 mo yeni tandelaeyeke halimaęž‰ make Yesu na handeekeme. Pa ekipeke wandaęž‰hali wopu koto paęž‰taęž‰ mombelemeke handa Yesu ambaęž‰ peekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Wetepenaęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ hande hali handaęž‰ wia alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Ame neketaęž‰ epeke loke haleme. Hoke hau paa na peaęž‰peke. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau tieke aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 15 Koto leekeeki opua hande hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao pua mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya yeni tandelaeyaęž‰ halitaęž‰ Yesue leekeme.  
\v 16 Kotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ yeni tandelaeyeke ekinaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu tanda haluekemaęž‰ kini pu mimikime.  
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ hoto paeyao e poko halaęž‰me. Kutupu halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make e pokolome leekeme.  
\v 18 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu luekemaęž‰ mineke pankemekeeki daeyaemekeme. Do ekinaęž‰yeke pimikime. Yesumaęž‰ hande Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ halaęž‰me leeke ekimaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone halome laa leekeme.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hande Eiyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone hone wia hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰ pu halaęž‰me. Hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ pu halaęž‰eki kone hande Eiyekemaęž‰ make pu halaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pu halaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao hande Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ walo halaęž‰me. Iki penkilipaęž‰tia pomuemenaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hau tiekemanu dupikieki wetepeao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ walieke.  
\v 21 Hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali mea daęž‰taasaęž‰ tupaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone hande Eiyekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone wia wandaęž‰hali mea daęž‰taasaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Kutupa make Apaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu na piki ipikaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ homeke pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰yeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ pi laaseme tupaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ pi make koto tupaęž‰ kone laenaęž‰yeke laęž‰laęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ pi na laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki tapaalaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ pi kone na laasaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pimanu opuaataęž‰ IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ make hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki miniki halaęž‰me. Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰lao daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki ambaęž‰ miniki halaęž‰eki yolo hataęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na pelieke.  
\v 25 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ nate epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate ambaęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opiteleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ daęž‰tilimikie.  
\v 26 Hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki kone daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ teke hali halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke make ipiki kone daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ teke hali haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 27 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke haleke handaataęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaalo paęž‰laęž‰ hali ipikaęž‰ Atekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 28 Do ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone eleke eleke na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ambaęž‰ homa lapaęž‰ peleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opulu peleme nate epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 29 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ lapaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao hamaęž‰ nane ipilimikie. Epeke hau pu hao homemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tiao daęž‰ta halimikie. Kutupa hoke hau pu hao homemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tiao pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nane pelimikie.   
\s1 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ wekitisi haemekeeki  
\p
\v 30 IĚ±maęž‰ ya kone hone wia hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kitaęž‰laęž‰eki IĚ±maęž‰ opuaataęž‰ pi yokaalu pitolome. Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ hone na wiki IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ halinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ hone witolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi yokaalu pitolo ekitaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 31 Ya pitolo ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kone wekitisi hao loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo ekitaęž‰ teke na wilieke.  
\v 32 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ pitolo ekinaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ wekitisi hao lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ lolo paęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki alaęž‰me hone witolome.  
\v 33 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliweki tapaemekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ hau piteleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme.  
\v 34 IĚ±maęž‰ pitolo ekimanu wekitisi hali muluekemaęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki muemenaęž‰yeke do pi alo loaęž‰me.  
\v 35 Dionitaęž‰ hande olaęž‰pake tupaęž‰ kaęž‰wa endialeke handaa paĚ±aĚ± wopu pu hayaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hosiki haluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone piaęž‰me.  
\v 36 Kutu piaęž‰pate yaka wekitisi hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ wekitisi hataęž‰ la kiaęž‰ ekimanu wetepeaalo paęž‰laęž‰eki kone halaęž‰me. Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pionoyeke waleaęž‰ e manutaęž‰ pokolo hataęž‰ pitoloeki manumaęž‰ kone yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaalaęž‰eki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao walaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 37 Kutupa IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ make yaka pi lawaasaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maketaęž‰ hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na opiki ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke make hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na handelememe.  
\v 38 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na tulaaseme ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.  
\v 39 Deto halaęž‰eki handaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Baibolo buka pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ teke weitelemepatetaęž‰ mo hande Baibolo buka pi manumaęž‰ kone yaka pi lawaasaęž‰me.  
\v 40 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke kiaasememe.   
\p
\v 41 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ yaka pi laenaęž‰yeke na weitolopate  
\v 42 ikitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ handoaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleme ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.  
\v 43 IĚ±taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ epolopate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na handaęž‰ minelememe. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki hali handaęž‰ milimikie.  
\v 44 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ pi lao alualu piteleme ekitaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰pate hande homeke halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na witelememe. Kutu piteleme ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honetaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ekipa tulaalimikipe.  
\v 45 IĚ±maęž‰ iki yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ samani pulueke hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hande ikaęž‰ hone tulaaleme hali Mosesitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone iki samani pilieke.  
\v 46 Mosesimaęž‰ leeke pimanu otaęž‰ekie laa hone tulaemekenaęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka pimanu make opulu pimime. Mosesimaęž‰ wape pieke ekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kone pieke ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 47 Kutu pulu pimipate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wape pieke ekimanu ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na tulaaleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi manutaęž‰ ekipa hone tulaalimikipe.   
\c 6  
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ 5 daoseni wandaęž‰hali ne haleekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰13-21, Maka 6ęž‰30-44, Luku 9ęž‰10-17)  
\p
\v 1 Koto pimanu laataęž‰ mo hande tunkulaęž‰pa pitieke Kaęž‰lili ikali mone teaęž‰naęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme. Koto ikali biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Taibitiasi lo halaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo yeni haemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni tandeleaaso hataęž‰ wele wopu pieke ekimanu handemeke ekinaęž‰ Yesu teliaęž‰ mea pemekeme.  
\v 3 Yesutaęž‰ eli maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰meiya pua ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pitimikime.  
\v 4 Hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke nate ipuluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ peekeme.  
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pea handaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao epemekeeki handataęž‰ Pilipi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ ne anaęž‰naęž‰ halomanaęž‰yeke netaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ hambomanaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 6 Pilipimaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pulu piekeeki ambaęž‰ hone wiekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Pilipimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ne hosikisiki kone nenaęž‰yeke palaowa hambaasotaęž‰ 200 kina kone anaęž‰ na pilieke.  
\v 8 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Saimono Pidanaęž‰ hameke Aęž‰ndutumaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 9 Do halaęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ bali palaowa punka yunki hataęž‰ make taęž‰peli yaapo make wia halaęž‰pate do wandaęž‰hali paeyao yolo hataęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ napeke na yelieke.  
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali pitiniao pitininaęž‰ lape leekeme. Nomaęž‰ wopu opaęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ pitimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao pitimikipate haliweki paeyao diminiekepate 5 daoseni tupaęž‰ pitimikime.  
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ hande palaowa meataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laataęž‰ mo pitimiki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ teli teli peaeyekeme. Mo hande taęž‰peli yaapo make koto tupaęž‰ teli teli peaeyekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao ikaęž‰ hone pieke tupaęž‰ kone mea nemekeme.  
\v 12 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao ne naa weleke hao pitinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande ne putupilikimanu minolotaęž‰ popusunu kone na winaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 13 Koto leeke handa mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hande bali palaowa yunki hataęž‰ nemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ naa winaęž‰ lemeke putupilikimanu paeyao mea basekede nunaęž‰ mendimikipate 12 basekede numanu tumbaemekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ wele wopu piekeeki hando hao alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ hande kenkenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ Potopede hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 15 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ kone Yesu taęž‰nkaęž‰paęž‰ mina ikaęž‰ kini hali haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ hone wimikieki Yesumaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰siki paa laęž‰kaęž‰la mo yu eli paęž‰taęž‰manu peekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ikali manda peekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰22-33, Maka 6ęž‰45-52)  
\p
\v 16 Welealo nanetaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekitaęž‰ oni tunkulaęž‰pa pitieke ikali kendo paęž‰taęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niaotaęž‰  
\v 17 kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ pua pita Kapeneami nane poluekemaęž‰ mo ikali tunkula pemekeme. Kutupa timbaęž‰ leekepate Yesutaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na opolo peekeme.  
\v 18 Kutupa pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ po tilipu tieke ipulu hataęž‰ ikali ho aęž‰meiyekeme.  
\v 19 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ deli awa tia 5 kilomida o 6 kilomida tupaęž‰ pemekepate Yesutaęž‰ kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ ipuluekemaęž‰ ikali manda anke hao epeekeeki handaataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ wopu homemekeme.  
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke dotaęž‰ IĚ±e leekeme.  
\v 21 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo kawaso tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu epenaęž‰e hone wimikime. Kutupa mo hande kawasotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ opolo polo pimiki alenaęž‰ kuta kone opolo pemekeme.   
\s1 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu weimikieki  
\p
\v 22 Kutupa da kelepeeketaęž‰ hande tunkulaęž‰pa pitieke ikali mone teaęž‰naęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kawaso homeke wiekeeki ambaęž‰ hone wimikime. Mo disaipolo haliwekitaęž‰ Yesu iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ na pitiki pa ikaęž‰ kone pemekeeki make hone wimikime.  
\v 23 Mandane kawaso manutaęž‰ Taibitiasi nane hao aęž‰paataęž‰ hande Tekehalimaęž‰ keiyae pi laa mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ palaowa teli teli peaeyeke ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ kone opolo epemekeme.  
\v 24 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu na hayekeeki make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki na haemekeeki make handaataęž‰ kawaso manunaęž‰ pita Kapeneami da nane Yesu weilu pemekeme.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ palaowa konee  
\p
\v 25 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo hande tunkulaęž‰pa pitieke ikali mone teaęž‰naęž‰ hayekeeki handaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Do paęž‰taęž‰ handimaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe lemekeme.  
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hande wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki puaęž‰eki handeme ekinaęž‰ IĚ± weiya mea na epeke hande palaowa naa weleke haemeke ekinaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ IĚ± weiya mea ipulimime.  
\v 27 Paeyaęž‰peke ne muluekemaęž‰ hone anepu na wiki pa u hapekeeki muluekemaęž‰ hone wotu wiaęž‰peke. Koto ekitaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone hoto paeyao pa u halieke. Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ koto netaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mea kilieke.   
\p
\v 28 Koto leeke handa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ eki pulumaęž‰pe.  
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa puemenaęž‰yeke hone paęž‰laęž‰me la Kodaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaminaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 30 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulamonoyeke eki wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handomono pilipikipe lemekeme.  
\v 31 Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰ mo hande hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ hande maęž‰na netiki pu haemekeme. Hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ Palaowa nenaęž‰yeke hepeni nane hataęž‰ halaęž‰niaeyekeme.  
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Mosesimaęž‰taęž‰ hepeni nane palaowa iki na kitolo piaęž‰me. Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ hepeni nane otaęž‰ palaowataęž‰ iki kiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 33 Do hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ palaowataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hepeni minaęž‰paęž‰lao holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰paataęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 34 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aneke halio kutupiki palaowataęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao ku hapeke.  
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ palaowataęž‰ IĚ± konee laataęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ paa na homilieke. Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikali naęž‰naęž‰ paa na pilieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 36 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ handaa kone hone na tulaasememe.  
\v 37 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ na tolu lueke.  
\v 38 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ oli hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰pa yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ na epeke IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ halinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ epolo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 39 IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ halinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do hau pionoyeke tapaalaęž‰me dupae. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na alupaake hande paelie dinaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ pa mea tiawaanoyeke tapaalaęž‰me.  
\v 40 Yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki dupae. Eiyeke handaa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki minaęž‰yeke hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo hande paelie dinaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali pa mea tiawaalueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 41 Yesumaęž‰ mo hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao epoaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ palaowataęž‰ IĚ± konee leeke ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ tulu tulu leekeme.  
\v 42 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ Yesue la Diosepenaęž‰ eiyeke na halaęž‰pe laataęž‰ inkiki ateke yaapo ambaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me. Ekipeke IĚ±taęž‰ oli hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao epoaęž‰me alaęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 43 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tulu tulu aleme pi paapaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 44 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke. Kutupa koto halitaęž‰ mo hande paelie dinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pa mea tiawaalueke.  
\v 45 Mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki dupae. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao walaęž‰ tiaalieke wape paęž‰laęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ hande Apaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke leekeme.  
\v 46 IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekinaęž‰ alomaęž‰ hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande Apaęž‰ otaęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ yaapo hao do aęž‰pa halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ homeke handaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 47 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome laataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰me.  
\v 48 Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ palaowataęž‰ IĚ±e laataęž‰  
\v 49 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ maęž‰na palaowa nemekepate homemekeme.  
\v 50 Kutu pimikipate oli hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao epeeke palaowataęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ koto palaowa neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na homilieke.  
\v 51 Oli hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ palaowataęž‰ IĚ±e leekeme. Hali epimaęž‰ do palaowa neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halieke. Kutupa mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ halo polo palaowataęž‰ yaka loke mindiki kone halueke. Kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰yeke yaka loke mindiki halueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 52 Koto leekeeki opuataęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ape la alu alu pitolo alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke mindiki nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nomonoyeke ekipa kiliepe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 53 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke ipikaęž‰ loke mindiki make ipikaęž‰ we make na nemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki na milimikie.  
\v 54 Hali epimaęž‰ yaka loke mindiki make yaka we make neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hande paelie dinaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pa mea tiawaalueke.  
\v 55 IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Yaka loke mindikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ nee kutupa yaka we make otaęž‰ ikalie leekeme.  
\v 56 Hali epimaęž‰ yaka loke mindiki make yaka we make neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ halieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ halueke.  
\v 57 Daęž‰ta halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa ipiki halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ IĚ± make halome. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ IĚ± haloaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ daęž‰ta halieke.  
\v 58 Koto ekinaęž‰ do ekitaęž‰ hande hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰niao aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ palaowae laataęž‰ hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰mei amedamaęž‰ naa homemeke palaowa tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ do palaowa neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halieke leekeme.  
\v 59 Do laęž‰laęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo Kapeneami nane hayeke pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ waleeke pimanue.   
\s1 Mo daęž‰tao halaęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 60 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki wopumaęž‰ koto leekeeki opua alotaęž‰ Do pitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ wopu piki pie. Epi amedamaęž‰ opuaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 61 Koto haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ tulu tulu lemekeeki Yesumaęž‰ hone wia kone mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do alo pinaęž‰ ki hone witelemepe.  
\v 62 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hao epeaęž‰ nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la polo paęž‰laęž‰eki handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki piliepe.  
\v 63 Loke mindikimaęž‰taęž‰ niki tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yelieke. Mo hande Sipitidimaęž‰ kone daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ Sipitidinaęž‰eki make daęž‰taapekeeki make loaęž‰me.  
\v 64 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate iki ameĚ±leĚ± haleme mandane haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaasememe leekeme. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaalo peleme haliwekitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone hone wiekeme. Ipiki linaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo polo pieke hali make ambaęž‰ kone hone wiekeme.  
\v 65 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ na peaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto hali IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 66 Koto leeke handaa Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki wopumaęž‰ Yesu kiao minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± paa na pomu haemekeme.  
\v 67 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ hande 12 disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make IĚ± kiao pelimikipe.  
\v 68 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Epi paęž‰taęž‰ pomonope. Nakaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ daęž‰tao halaęž‰ pimanue.  
\v 69 Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Yakopiki Hali hale ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulao hao ambaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 70 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki 12 haliwekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na talopu mea haminaęž‰ loeke yekea. Kutu puaęž‰pate iki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ hali homeketaęž‰ hoke temoko halaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 71 Koto leeke ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Isekatioti hali Saimononaęž‰ eiyeke Diudasi paęž‰taęž‰ leekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ hande 12 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke hali kone wetepetaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeekeme.   
\c 7  
\s1 Yesu make ipikaęž‰ hameke titi ameĚ±leĚ± haemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Kutu pieke hoki nanetaęž‰ Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki lu pimiki hone wimiki handaa Yesutaęž‰ Diudia nane pomuluekemaęž‰ hone na wiki mo Kaęž‰lili nane pomiekeme.  
\v 2 Hande Sale damanu paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke ekinaęž‰ ne pambolo pimiki di tekepaęž‰taęž‰ yeekeme.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hameke titimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pitele ekimanu handenaęž‰yeke do paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao Diudia nane puaęž‰peke.  
\v 4 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ yaka pitoloeki handenaęž‰e hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aęž‰mbao hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do haumanu pitele ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke lemekeme.  
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke titimaęž‰ kone Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaemekeme.  
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka nate aĚ±iĚ± na aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 7 Kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ki hone wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ piteleme haumanu hoke ekie laa lo halo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ki hone witelememe.  
\v 8 Ikitaęž‰ hande ne pambolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ puaęž‰paęž‰peke. IĚ±taęž‰ yaka nate aĚ±iĚ± na aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ na polueke leekeme.  
\v 9 Koto pi laataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane pa hayekeme.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ hande Sale da manunaęž‰ ne pambaemeke paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 10 Ipikaęž‰ hameke titi hande ne pambolo pimikieki paęž‰taęž‰ pemeke hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesu make peneme yao na peke aęž‰mbao peekeme.  
\v 11 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hande ne pambeeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ Yesu weitolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 12 Mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ hambiliki hambilikimaęž‰ pimikime. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ epeke halie lemekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Diaęž‰me laa Wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ya pi lo halaęž‰ halie lemekeme.  
\v 13 Koto lemekepate wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pa hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ peneme yao na leekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Hande ne pambemekeeki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ pua hataęž‰ pi waleekeme.  
\v 15 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ penkilipitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ sukulu na piki halimaęž‰ kone wopu handa ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do walolo ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone wia yakaeki na walolome. IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki kone walolome.  
\v 17 Hali epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do waloloeki Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki kone walaasoeki make o yaka hone wia waloloeki make handaęž‰ wilieke.  
\v 18 Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone wia pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki kone aęž‰meiyaasaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki kone na aęž‰meiyaake ipiki tapaalaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki aęž‰meiyaluekemaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ yayapiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ hali diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ halie.  
\v 19 Hande Lo Pi manutaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ na kaęž‰laęž‰pe. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande Lo Pimanu na opitolo pitaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± lia homaaluekemaęž‰ ekipeke pitelemepe.   
\p
\v 20 Mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pilaęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ epimaęž‰ luekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau homeke puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ penkilipimime.  
\v 22 Mosesimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wekisunu paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leeke ekinaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ make weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pilimikie. Mosesimaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰pate pa Mosesimaęž‰ do hau na kini pu miekeme. Ikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ atekemeimaęž‰ kini pu mimikime.  
\v 23 Mosesimaęž‰ waleeke Lo Pimanu yambaęž‰laamaęž‰naęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ kone weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ hali homeke epeaowaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ekipeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankelemepe.  
\v 24 Pa lekemaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ hone na wiki tiki tiki hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo.   
\s1 Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hande Ketisope  
\p
\v 25 Mandane Diutuseleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande luekemaęž‰ taapeleme halitaęž‰ do hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe.  
\v 26 Handaęž‰pe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pi alaęž‰pate ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pi na alaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ do halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso hone witelemepe.  
\v 27 Pate do hali hao epaęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolomaęž‰pate hande Ketiso epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hao epaęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yelieke laa lemekeme.   
\p
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ pi walolo wi la alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ handelemepe. IĚ± hao epolo alenaęž‰ make handelemepe. Yaka kone hone wia na epoaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lo halaęž‰me.  
\v 29 Koto halitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handelemepate ipiki yaapo hao epoaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ handolome leekeme.  
\v 30 Koto leeketaęž‰ ipiki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minuluekemaęž‰ pimikipate ipikaęž‰ nate aĚ±iĚ± diaęž‰yeke handaa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki na miniekeme. Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 31 Hande Ketiso epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do halinaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ankulaliepe lemekeme.   
\s1 Haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minulu paęž‰naęž‰ tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 32 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ koto pi lemeke ekimanu mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ opuataęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minulu penaęž‰ mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliweki tapaemekeme.  
\v 33 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki ameĚ±leĚ± hosiki haotaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ polueke.  
\v 34 IĚ± weilu pelemepate IĚ± halo polo alenaęž‰ iki epaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ± na handaęž‰ wilimiki leekeme.  
\v 35 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi laęž‰ alu alu pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handolo polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hane poluekemaęž‰ alaęž‰pe. Ipikitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haleme Kitiki daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu mo Kitiki wandaęž‰hali walo peliekepe.  
\v 36 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ weilu pelemepate IĚ± na handaęž‰ wilimikie laa kutupa IĚ± halo polo alenaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me la leaęž‰me lemekeme. Eki epinaęž‰ leaęž‰pe lemekeme.   
\s1 Deto halaęž‰ ikalinaęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 37 Mo hande ne pambemekeeki paeyeke natenaęž‰ nate tieke yeekeme. Koto natenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ tia liao hataęž‰ pi anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ ikali nenaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 38 Mo Baibolo bukamaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ikali opa wotu yapilieke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 39 Yesumaęž‰ koto leeke ekitaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ kone leekeme. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi muluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ leekeme. Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halo pieke kapu tieke aĚ±iĚ± diaęž‰yeke handaa mo Holi Sipitidi aĚ±iĚ± na epenaęž‰ leekeme.   
\s1 Wandaęž‰hali putupa alu alu pea taęž‰taęž‰ haemekeeki  
\p
\v 40 Mo mombaęž‰la haemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opua alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Potopede hali otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 41 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ hande Ketisoe lemekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ketiso epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane hao na ipilieke lemekeme.  
\v 42 Pa ekipeke mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ Deipidi tapake hali hataęž‰taęž‰ hande Deipiti hao hayeke daoni paęž‰taęž‰ Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ daoni paęž‰taęž‰ mendilieke la laęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 43 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ putupa alualu pea taęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.  
\v 44 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minuluekemaęž‰ hone wimikipate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki na miniekeme.   
\s1 You haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaemekeeki  
\p
\v 45 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke alenaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pemekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰ hande tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande halitaęž‰ ekipeke daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ mina na hatuku ipulimipe lemekeme.   
\p
\v 46 Mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ambaęž‰ hataęž‰ make do halimaęž‰ alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki pi na leekeme.  
\v 47 Mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ make makeao pia.  
\v 48 Nikaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make Paęž‰tisi hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao pia. Diaęž‰me.  
\v 49 Do da wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Lo Pimanu na handeleme ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ hone ambaęž‰ wiekeme.   
\p
\v 50 Hande ambaęž‰ kone Yesu handolo peeke hali Nikodimasimaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 51 Nikaęž‰ Lo Pi manumaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa hameke pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ pi opuataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pieke hau handaęž‰ wia pitolotaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 52 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki lu pambaaso alotaęž‰ Neke make mo hande Kaęž‰lili hali yekea. Mo Baibolo buka yataęž‰pataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ oli Kaęž‰lili nane hao epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki na handilipikie lemekeme.  
\v 53 [Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyao da pemekeme.]   
\c 8  
\s1 Tooli kaęž‰taalu pitolo pitinaęž‰ handeeke wandaęž‰ hatuku epeekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ da pemekepate Yesutaęž‰ mo Olipi pote paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.  
\v 2 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki ipikitaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali wopu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mombelemeke handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pitiniao pitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi waleekeme.  
\v 3 Mo hande Lo Pimanu walo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao wandaęž‰ homeke hatuku mea aęž‰pa haliweki ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ haenaęž‰ lemekeme. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ tooli kaęž‰taalu pitolo haenaęž‰ handeeke ekinaęž‰ hatuku epemekeme.  
\v 4 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Do wandaęž‰maęž‰ tooli kaęž‰taalu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitolo haenaęž‰ kone handemekeme.  
\v 5 Mosesimaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu walolo alotaęž‰ Dupiki wandaęž‰taęž‰ toopimaęž‰ lia homaapaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ eki pi lelipikipe lemekeme.  
\v 6 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ weitolo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰eki opuluekemaęž‰ yokaemekeme. Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao pitaęž‰ kiki maĚ±lekemaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ wape wape piekeme.  
\v 7 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ tialiao hataęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hoke hau na paęž‰laęž‰ hali hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰la toopimaęž‰ do wandaęž‰ linaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 8 Koto laa paa pandaęž‰puniao pitaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ wape piekeme.  
\v 9 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ koto pi opuataęž‰ homeke la la pu takaęž‰laake haliweki ambaęž‰la homeke la la pu paeyao pemekeme. Yesu homeke pa pitinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ pa tiao hayekeme.  
\v 10 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tialiao hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Mo hande haliwekitaęž‰ handopaęž‰taęž‰ halemepe. Hali homekemaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu na pitaęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 11 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make neke yaapo pi yokaalu na pulueke. Puaataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaęž‰peke leekeme.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±  
\p
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±e. Hali epimaęž‰ ya hoki nane teliaęž‰ mea epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ lo pambaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na pomiki paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ daęž‰ta halieke. Mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halieke.  
\v 13 Mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ piteleeki nakaęž‰ kone la kitele ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi na aleme lemekeme.  
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ pitoloeki IĚ±maęž‰ kone la kuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. IĚ± hao epoaęž‰eki make wetepenaęž‰ polo polo alenaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ handolopate IĚ± hao epoaęž‰eki make wetepenaęž‰ polo polo alenaęž‰ make iki na handelememe.  
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu piteleme ekitaęž‰ kenke haliwekimaęž‰ yaalo alememe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu na pitolopate  
\v 16 pi yokaalu pulueke laa puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰eki pitolo hataęž‰ pulueke. Ekipeke na loaęž‰me. Ya siki na hake IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali yaka Apaęž‰ yaapo halopaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Ikaęž‰ Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ wape peleme ekitaęž‰ dupae. La halaęž‰laęž‰ hali yaapomaęž‰ homeke pi lepekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki alepeme.  
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ pitoloeki ya kone la kitolome. Kutupa IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ make yaka pi lawaasaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± make yaka Apaęž‰ make iki na handelememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± handemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ make handolo pimime leekeme.   
\p
\v 20 Koto leeke pi manutaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo mo mani wimiki tembolo da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ nate aĚ±iĚ± diaęž‰yeke handaa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki na daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniekeme.   
\s1 IĚ± pulu alenaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeeki  
\p
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ polueke. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± weilu pelemepate ikaęž‰ hoke hau taapunaęž‰ hao homilimikie. IĚ± pulu alenaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 22 Koto leeke handaa mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± pulu alenaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki kone luekemaęž‰ leaęž‰pe lemekeme.  
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ do oto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme haliweki halemepate IĚ±taęž‰ manda hao epoaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hao haleme haliweki halemepate IĚ±taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Koto peleme ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau taapunaęž‰ hao homilimikie laa loaęž‰me. IĚ± do halimaęž‰ alo pi na opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ hoke hau taapunaęž‰ hao homilimikie leekeme.  
\v 25 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ epipe lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Hande titi panake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ loaęž‰eki kone alo loaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Ikaęž‰ pu haleme haunaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi wopu lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ halinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ekie. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ opuaęž‰eki kone kenke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la halolome leekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo Ateke leeke ekitaęž‰ hone na wimikime.  
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke mea aęž‰meiyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± do halimaęž‰ laęž‰tiki puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa koto natenaęž‰ hone wilimikie. Kutupa make IĚ±maęž‰ ya kone hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ waleaęž‰eki homeke pu haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wilimikie.  
\v 29 Kutupa IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ halitaęž‰ dikaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ halopaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaaso hau hoto paeyao pu halo ekinaęž‰ IĚ± honumake hano IĚ± na minaęž‰paęž‰lalaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 30 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ do leeke pi opuaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.   
\s1 Mo hande otaęž‰ pimanu opiteleme ekimaęž‰ iki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ haminaęž‰ leliekeeki  
\p
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ waloloeki opua peaęž‰tiki pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ ya disaipolo haliweki hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 32 otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handilimikie. Kutupa mo otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao haminaęž‰ lelieke.  
\v 33 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapake haliweki halomaęž‰pate hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ talaęž‰liao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pa hameke na pokao haomaęž‰me laa Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halimikie ale ekitaęž‰ eki epinaęž‰ alepe lemekeme.  
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ hoke hau pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pu halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ e pa hameke pokaasaęž‰ hali leke halaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 35 Kutu piki halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke halinaęž‰ tapake ameĚ±leĚ± hoto paeyao na hao hatiki piliepate teke halinaęž‰ eiyeketaęž‰ hoto paeyao hao halieke.  
\v 36 Hande Eiyekemaęž‰ iki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halimikie.  
\v 37 Ikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ tapake haleme ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handolopate IĚ±maęž‰ walolo pimanu na mendieleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ± luekemaęž‰ pitelememe.  
\v 38 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰eki kone IĚ±maęž‰ walolopate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ waleaęž‰eki pitelememe leekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰e lemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ wekitonu haemekenaęž‰ yolutaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ pieke ekimanu kone pulu pimime.  
\v 40 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ opuaęž‰eki homeke otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± luekemaęž‰ pitelememe. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki hau na piekeme.  
\v 41 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ piekeeki kone pitelememe. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ pake wekitonu diaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ homeke Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 42 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo pimime. IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hao aęž‰pa ame do halo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Ya hone wia na epeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyeke aęž‰pa halo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 43 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ ekipeke hone na witelemepe. IĚ±maęž‰ aloeki na opulumeke hone witeleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 44 Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Sadaninaęž‰ eiyeke titi halememe. Koto peleme ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu puluekemaęž‰ pitelememe. Titi panake paęž‰taęž‰ kone ipikitaęž‰ hali litaęž‰laęž‰ hali hayekeme. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hau peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Yayapiki pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki kone alaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yayapiki pi lo halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make ipikitaęž‰ yayapiki pi alaęž‰ teke hali halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make loaęž‰me.  
\v 45 IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na opitelememe.  
\v 46 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hoke hau puaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ peneme yaaliepe. IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke na opitelemepe.  
\v 47 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki tonumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu opu halemepate ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki na haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ na opitelememe.   
\s1 Yesu Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo  
\p
\v 48 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ Sametia hali neke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paeki lomaęž‰ekea.  
\v 49 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko diaęž‰me. Yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ pi laasopate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka pi tombaaluekemaęž‰ pitelememe.  
\v 50 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi kone na laasopate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yaka pi laluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰pate ipikitaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ halie.  
\v 51 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ yaka waloloeki opua piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki na handilieke.  
\v 52 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone witolomaęž‰me. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pilaęž‰me. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ make mo potopede haliweki make ambaęž‰ homemekepate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ yaka waloloeki opua pitaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki na handilieke lepate  
\v 53 nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ homeekeme laa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki ankulaluekemaęž‰ alepe. Kutupa mo hande potopede haliweki make ambaęž‰ homemekeme laa neketaęž‰ ekipiki hali haluekemaęž‰ hone witolo alepe lemekeme.   
\p
\v 54 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kone yaka pi laa laowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pa hali kone halo puaęž‰me. Yaka pi laasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ kone laasaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me leme halie.  
\v 55 Ipikitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handelemepate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki halaęž‰eki handolome. Ipikitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na handolome loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki tupaęž‰ yayapiki hali halo puaęž‰me. Kutu pulu puaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi make opu halome.  
\v 56 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ yaka di handuluekemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa hataęž‰ handaataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.  
\v 57 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ bapi manutaęž‰ pa 50manu aĚ±iĚ± na paelaęž‰pate Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ handekea.  
\v 58 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na mendieke natenaęž‰ kone IĚ±taęž‰ pa halome leekeme.  
\v 59 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu luekemaęž‰ toopimanu mimikipate Yesutaęž‰ mo tembolo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao aęž‰mbao hamaęž‰ nane peekeme.   
\c 9  
\s1 Inkikimaęž‰ mendieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone handaęž‰peke na yeke halinaęž‰ leke ki laeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ handeekepate inkikimaęž‰ mendieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone leke holupiki hali handeekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Disao. Do mendieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone do halinaęž‰ leke holupiki hautaęž‰ epimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa ateke inkikinaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o ipikaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone paęž‰laęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 3 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰ make ateke inkikimaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekinaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ do hali epeaasaęž‰eki handenaęž‰yeke leke holupiki hali mendia paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 4 Hande IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ halinaęž‰ etaęž‰ nate aęž‰pa talo haenaęž‰ pokatiki pumanaęž‰e. Timbaęž‰ lolo yapeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaapeke na yelieke.  
\v 5 IĚ± kenkenaęž‰ aęž‰pa halo dinaęž‰taęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasoeki halome leekeme.  
\v 6 Kotoeki laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ dopi kenkenaęž‰ taataęž‰ kenke taapu dakole peao handeeki meaataęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ kitaaso hataęž‰  
\v 7 ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande tunkulaęž‰ pa ulaęž‰ Sailoaęž‰me ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua nakaęž‰ leke popeleke tandaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme. Koto ikali bikitaęž‰ Tapaalaęž‰me laa lo haemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hali puataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke tandaęž‰pa alaęž‰taęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la paa epeekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ da wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make mo pitu hataęž‰ honke leaęž‰tiki piekeeki opimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ hande pitu hataęž‰ honke lo pitaęž‰tiki piaęž‰ hali diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lemekeme.  
\v 9 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Koto hali lataa lemekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Do halimaęž‰ handeke hali kone maęž‰ndaęž‰ hataęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme. Koto lemekepate mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ IĚ± lataa leekeme.  
\v 10 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ekipa nakaęž‰ leke epeao paęž‰laęž‰pe la lemekepate  
\v 11 ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Yesu biki leleme halimaęž‰ kenke dakole peao yaka lekenaęž‰ kitao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Sailoaęž‰me ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua nakaęž‰ leke popeleke tandaęž‰paęž‰peke leaęž‰me laa koto leeke handaa IĚ± pua tandepoaęž‰pate alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone handoaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 12 Koto leeke handaa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Koto halitaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe la lemekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome leekeme.   
\s1 Mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ hande epeaeyekeeki handemekeeki  
\p
\v 13 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ hande ambaęž‰ leke holupiki hali hatuku mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ waluekemaęž‰ mea pemekeme.  
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ kenke dakole peao mo halinaęž‰ leke kilaake hautaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ mo hali paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ leketaęž‰ ekipa epeao paęž‰laęž‰pe la lotaęž‰ pimiki handaa mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kenke dakole piki ekimaęž‰ yaka lekenaęž‰ kitaeyeketaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua tandepoaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ handolome leekeme.  
\v 16 Mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hau paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ na tapaalaęž‰me lemekepate mandane haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dupiki wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ ekipa piliepe la lemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone putupaalu pea pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ lemekeme.   
\p
\v 17 Kutupa mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ hande hali paęž‰taęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka leke kilaeyaęž‰me alepatetaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ eki hone witelepe lemekeme. Mo halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potopede halie la leekepate  
\v 18 mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke holu pea hayekeeki make mo leke epeaeyekeeki make koto pi opuaęž‰peke kiaaso hataęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ ateke inkiki yaapo wi laęž‰ mea  
\v 19 ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ wekipe. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ panake mendi paęž‰taęž‰ kone leke holupiki weki mendipe laataęž‰ Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ekipa handolo piaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 20 Mo halinaęž‰ ateke inkiki yaapomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto halitaęž‰ dikaęž‰ weki yaęž‰laęž‰pate mendiaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone leke holupiki weki mendiaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone ulupaęž‰patetaęž‰  
\v 21 ame ipikaęž‰ leke kila handaęž‰laęž‰eki make ipikaęž‰ leke kilaake hautaęž‰ epimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe. Kotaęž‰ dikitaęž‰ mataęž‰laęž‰me laa lepekeme. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua opuaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ipikaęž‰ bapi manutaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone la kilieke laa lepekeme.  
\v 22 Ateke inkiki yaapomaęž‰ mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ dupa lepekeme. Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ hande Ketiso halaęž‰me lelimi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰yeke pa yokomanaęž‰ la pi laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homepekeme.  
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo toolimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikaęž‰ bapimanu anaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua opuaęž‰pe laa lepekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Kutupa hoto yaapo peao hande mendieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone leke holupiki halitaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ wi la ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰eki lapeke laa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me. Koto hande halitaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ halie la lemekeme.  
\v 25 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ halipe. IĚ± mataęž‰laęž‰me. Pa hau homeketaęž‰ handolome. Ambaęž‰taęž‰ yaka leke holu pea haowaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ yaka leke kila handolome leekeme.  
\v 26 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neke paęž‰taęž‰ eki hau piaęž‰pe. Nakaęž‰ leketaęž‰ ekipa kilaeyaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimiki handaa  
\v 27 mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ambaęž‰ la kuaęž‰pate na opuelememe. Ekipeke pa opuluekemaęž‰ alemepe laa iki make mo hande halinaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki haluekemaęž‰ hone witelemepe la leekeme.  
\v 28 Koto leeke handaa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki kitaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo hande halinaęž‰ disaipolo hali halepate nikitaęž‰ Mosesinaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki halomaęž‰me.  
\v 29 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰pate koto hande halitaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ hao aęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰pe. Niki na handolomaęž‰me laa lemekeme.   
\p
\v 30 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ hao aęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰pe alemepatetaęž‰ yaka leke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kilaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi na opitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handolomaęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau peaaseme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ opu halaęž‰me.  
\v 32 Kotaęž‰ panake paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wepieke paęž‰taęž‰ kone mo mendieke dinaęž‰ kone leke holupiki halinaęž‰ leke kilaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ dupaeyaęž‰me pitaęž‰ na opolomaęž‰me.  
\v 33 Koto hande halimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± hao na epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ hau homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yolo piaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰ hokeeki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰leke daele halimaęž‰ kone niki waluekemaęž‰ alepe lemekeme. Koto laa mo halitaęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰yeke pao yoka taęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ lemekeme.   
\s1 Hoke ekimaęž‰ leke holu peaasaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali yoka taęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ lelememe lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ mo hali weiya handaęž‰ wia ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halepe laa leeke handaa  
\v 36 mo halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao haluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ biki la kie leekepate  
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ handeme. Neke yaapo do pi pi alepe halie laa leekeme.  
\v 38 Mo halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Hone tulaasome laataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ tumiki yotuao pitiekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kenkenaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me la leke holupiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handenaęž‰ make handeleme wandaęž‰hali make leke holu pea haenaęž‰yeke epoaęž‰me la leekeme.  
\v 40 Mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ koto leekeeki opua Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ leke holupiki haliweki halememaęž‰ alepe lemekepate  
\v 41 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Leke holupiki haliweki haemekenaęž‰ yolutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulu piaęž‰me laa kutupulu piaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me aleme ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hokeeki pa ulaęž‰me leekeme.   
\c 10  
\s1 Mo Sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hoĚ±lindaęž‰naęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu hoĚ±lindaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ na peke pa paęž‰taęž‰ pondaęž‰pa peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ alemanu muluekemaęž‰ pake nalaęž‰ halie.  
\v 2 Pate mo potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pulaęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo hande sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke halaęž‰ halie leekeme.  
\v 3 Mo potaęž‰ kake handeteke halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ koto hali penaęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ lombalieke. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ biki laa wi laęž‰ mepi peaataęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane hatuku pelieke.  
\v 4 Hamaęž‰ nane hatuku puaataęž‰ ipiki ambaęž‰la titinaęž‰ pelieke. Kutupa mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opitolo hataęž‰ ipiki teliaęž‰ mea pelimikie.  
\v 5 Pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ teliaęž‰ meataęž‰ na pelimikie. Diaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make na opitolo hataęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu pindipa pelimikie.   
\p
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa do pi leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰ do pi teketaęž‰ hone na wimikime.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali  
\p
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ paa dupa leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. IĚ±taęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake halome.  
\v 8 IĚ± na epeke hano titinaęž‰ epemeke haliweki paeyaotaęž‰ pake nolo pimiki haliweki epemeke handaa hande sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi na opimikime.  
\v 9 IĚ±taęž‰ potaęž‰ kake halome. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halimaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki milieke. Kutupa mo halitaęž‰ tukiki nane puaęž‰tiki hamaęž‰ nane aęž‰paęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ epeke nemanu netiki pilieke.  
\v 10 Pake nalaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu pake meataęž‰ lia hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ ipilimipatetaęž‰ IĚ± epolo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki muemenaęž‰yeke epolome. Tumba ulaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone muemenaęž‰yeke epolome.   
\p
\v 11 IĚ±taęž‰ handaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke halo halie. Mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yaka daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki hone na ulueke.  
\v 12 Mo yenki e pokaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ pa maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke hawaaso hataęž‰ mo tikene kika epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ teke some diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pelieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo tikene kikamaęž‰ hande maęž‰naęž‰manu lu neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea pindipa pelimikie.  
\v 13 Hande yenki muluekemaęž‰ e pokeeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu na witolo hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pa e pokaasaęž‰ hali yaalo hataęž‰taęž‰ pindipa pelieke.  
\v 14-15 IĚ±taęž‰ hande maęž‰naęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke halo halie. Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰laęž‰eki make IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka Apaęž‰ handolo tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu handolome. Kutupa yaka sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ make IĚ± handilimikie. Kutupa hande sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ yaka daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki alupaowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke.  
\v 16 Yaka mandane maęž‰naęž‰manu make halememe. Do haleme ekimanu homeke na loaęž‰me. Iki make yaka pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opitolo haenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ minaęž‰neaalueke. Kutupa mo maęž‰naęž‰manu tapake homeke halo pelemepatetaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali make homeke kone halieke.   
\p
\v 17 Yaka daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone pa muluekemaęž‰ alupaalo poloeki yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ kotoeki handolo hataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wotu homaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 18 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yaka daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki hoeyaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate yaka hone wia kone yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ homeke anaęž‰naęž‰ kia pa IĚ±maęž‰ homeke anaęž‰naęž‰ paa meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do ekitaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰pekee laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ do pimanu leeke ekinaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ putupa taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.  
\v 20 Mandane haliweki wopumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me laa ipikitaęž‰ keaaso pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ekipeke opitelemepe laa leaęž‰tiki pimikipate  
\v 21 mandane haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hoke temoko pilaęž‰ halimaęž‰ dupiki pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa hoke temokomaęž‰taęž‰ leke holupiki haliwekinaęž‰ leke ekipa kilaaliepe laa leaęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\s1 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu kiaemekeeki  
\p
\v 22 Koto pitaęž‰ Diutuseleme nane haenaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki nate epeekeme. Koto natetaęž‰ di wia hao ambaęž‰ kone mo hande tembolo da potaęž‰ pa lombemekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ pimikime. Kosaęž‰ kinaęž‰ hataęž‰ pimikime.  
\v 23 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ mo Solomononaęž‰ da mineke paęž‰taęž‰ pomiekeme.  
\v 24 Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki dupao hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ hoto ekipunaęž‰ hone eleke eleke wia hamono lelipiki laataęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hande Ketisope. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi la kiaęž‰peke lemekeme.  
\v 25 Yesumaęž‰ iki pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ la kuaęž‰patetaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaalememe. Yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pitolo haumanu paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ yaka biki mea aęž‰meiyaasemepatetaęž‰  
\v 26 ikitaęž‰ yaka sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu na haleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaasememe.  
\v 27 Yaka sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ yaka pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make minelememe. IĚ±maęž‰ make iki handolome. Kutupa yaka hoki nane teliaęž‰ mea ipulimime.  
\v 28 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰eki halono ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na homilimikie. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ ya kiki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 29 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ iki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kiaęž‰me. Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰ make manda hataęž‰ paeyao ankulalaęž‰me. Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ miniki halaęž‰ ekimanu hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 30 Yaka Apaęž‰ dikitaęž‰ homeke kone halopaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 31 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu luekemaęž‰ toopimanu paa mimikime.  
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ peaalaęž‰ epeke pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu wotu IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰pate eki puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ IĚ± luekemaęž‰ pitelemepe.  
\v 33 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke peleeki maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ toopimaęž‰ neke luekemaęž‰ na pitolomaęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰ laasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ pa hali yaęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ kone alome le ekinaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ dupa wape pea ulaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ kodaęž‰sunue loaęž‰me laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 35 Kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰niaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ kodaęž‰manue laa leekeme. Kutupa Baibolo bukanaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki kone pa u halieke.  
\v 36 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±taęž‰ hande yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± meataęž‰ do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ epono IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke halome loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ laasopatemaęž‰ ekipeke alemepe.  
\v 37 Yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu na puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaapaęž‰pe.  
\v 38 Kutu puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaake hataęž‰ kone yaka pitolo ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ kone hone tulaapeke aleo. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande Apaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰eki make IĚ±taęž‰ ipiki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haloeki make handaęž‰ hone wilimikie leekeme.  
\v 39 Yesu pa daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minuluekemaęž‰ pimikipate ipikitaęž‰ opaęž‰ pa lopa peekeme.   
\p
\v 40 Yesutaęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua mo Diodani ikali tunkula mone teaęž‰naęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ bapitaisi peaatiki pu hayeke alenaęž‰ opolo puataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.  
\v 41 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua mombolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ wele wotu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki wopu na piekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ do hali paęž‰taęž‰ leeke pi paeyao ambaęž‰ yaalaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 42 Kutupa wandaęž‰hali wopu koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.   
\c 11  
\s1 Laęž‰satesi homeekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Bedani da paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali Laęž‰satesi yeni hayekeme. Mo Bedani dataęž‰ Mada hakepiki Meti yaaponaęž‰ dae.  
\v 2 Mo Metimaęž‰taęž‰ hande Tekehalinaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ totopo wotupiki senisi holaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ itikimaęž‰ kone honiaeyekeme. Koto wandaęž‰naęž‰ beliki Laęž‰satesi yeni hayekeme.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hakilaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakaęž‰ yankeketaęž‰ yeni hao ulaęž‰me laa tapaepekeme.  
\v 4 Yesumaęž‰ koto pi opua alotaęž‰ Koto yenimaęž‰taęž‰ hali na homaalieke laa koto yeni aęž‰pa hake hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ biki make mea aęž‰meiyaenaęž‰yeke aęž‰pa hao paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ mo belialaęž‰ tepo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu wiekeme.  
\v 6 Kutupa hande Laęž‰satesi yeni hao ulaęž‰me leekeeki opuataęž‰ pa hoto yaapo koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao  
\v 7 ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diudia nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pomanaęž‰e leekepate  
\v 8 ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Ambaęž‰ numaneke aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ neke luekemaęž‰ taapemepate koto paęž‰taęž‰ paa pomanaęž‰ alepe lemekeme.  
\v 9 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nate homekenaęž‰ pa yataęž‰peaęž‰peke nate leke manutaęž‰ 12 awamanu diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ oli nate talo haenaęž‰ pomiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ lopuluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰tia na pelieke laa  
\v 10 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰ timbaęž‰ alo haenaęž‰ pomiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± na peaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ lopuluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰tia pelieke leekeme.  
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ kotoeki laa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ alo alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ yankeke Laęž‰satesitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ u peilaęž‰patetaęž‰ ipiki mea tiaalo pulume leekeme.  
\v 12 Koto leeke handaa mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. U peliaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ tiaalieke lemekeme.  
\v 13 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Laęž‰satesi otaęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ pa u peileke alaęž‰me hone wimikime.  
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao alotaęž‰ Laęž‰satesi otaęž‰ homeekeme.  
\v 15 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulao haminaęž‰yeke iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ ipiki yaapo na haowaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolome laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pomanaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ Tomasitaęž‰ hande Mandaęž‰e halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo yankeketiti paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ Disa ameĚ±leĚ± paeyao mandakenaęž‰ bape laa ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± homomanaęž‰e leekeme.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ paa mea tiaasaęž‰eki make daęž‰taasaęž‰eki make halaęž‰me  
\p
\v 17 Yesu opolo puaataęž‰ Laęž‰satesi lapaęž‰ pea haenaęž‰taęž‰ hoto tonkopu wiekeeki opiekeme.  
\v 18 Mo Bedani dataęž‰ Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ kone hayekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa Diu wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Mada Meti yaapo ipilikaęž‰ anaęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ pi pi loluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.   
\p
\v 20 Madamaęž‰ Yesu ipulaęž‰me lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ mandaęž‰hande peekepate Metitaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ peekeme.  
\v 21 Madamaęž‰ Yesu mandaęž‰hande pea ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ haekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ya anaęž‰ na homolo piaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Kutu pulu piaęž‰pate pa ame do kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ honke lelipi ale Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ kilieke hone witolome leekeme.  
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ anaęž‰taęž‰ paa tiaalieke leekeme.  
\v 24 Madamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande paeliaęž‰ natenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paa mea tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone witolome leekeme.  
\v 25 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pa mea tiaasaęž‰eki make daęž‰taasaęž‰eki make halome. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hali homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kone daęž‰ta halieke.  
\v 26 Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na homilieke. IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pinaęž‰ homelepe laa leekeme.  
\v 27 Madamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Aowe. Nakaęž‰ kakemaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ neketaęž‰ hande Ketiso make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke do kenkenaęž‰ ipilieke leeke halitaęž‰ hone witolome leekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ eĚ± leekeeki  
\p
\v 28 Madamaęž‰ kotoeki laa pa pua hakepiki Meti paęž‰taęž‰ yopu pua alotaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ do aęž‰pa hataęž‰ neke wi alaęž‰me.  
\v 29 Meti koto pi opua tiao Yesu mandaęž‰hande puluekemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya peekeme.  
\v 30 Yesutaęž‰ mo hande da paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na opolo peke Madataęž‰ ipiki mandaęž‰hande pieke alenaęž‰ pa hayekeme.  
\v 31 Mo mandane Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Meti paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pitaęž‰taęž‰ Meti aĚ±iĚ± tiao hama peekeeki handaataęž‰ ipiki teliaęž‰ mea pemekeme. Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Metimaęž‰ mo lapaęž‰ pieke ale paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± lolo pulaęž‰me hone wimikime.  
\v 32 Metimaęž‰ Yesu hayeke alenaęž‰ opolo pua Yesu handolo ipikaęž‰ anke paęž‰taęž‰ lopaęž‰niao alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neke do paęž‰taęž‰ haekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ya anaęž‰ na homolo piaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 33 Metimaęž‰ eĚ± leekeeki make mo ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pemeke Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ eĚ± lemekeeki make handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki tetomaęž‰ homeekeme.  
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ wilimipe leeke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Handolo epoe lemekeme.  
\v 35 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ eĚ± leekeme.  
\v 36 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi hotiolo alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰pe. Do halimaęž‰ Laęž‰satesi paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wotu homolo pitaęž‰laęž‰me lemekepate  
\v 37 mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ hande leke holupiki halinaęž‰ leketaęž‰ kilaeyaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make saęž‰saęž‰ piaęž‰peke yolo piaęž‰me hone witolomaęž‰me lemekeme.   
\s1 Laęž‰satesi paa mea tiaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 38 Yesumaęž‰ pa puki tetomaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo lapaęž‰ pimiki alenaęž‰ peekeme. Mo lapaęž‰ pimiki ekitaęž‰ tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ toopimaęž‰ aęž‰mba wimikime.  
\v 39 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo toopi pa nane mea wipe leekepate hande hoieke halinaęž‰ beliki Madamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Punku wotu pilieke. Mo lapaęž‰ pea hamonotaęž‰ hoto tonkopu paeyaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 40 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulao haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki handilipikie pitaęž‰ na loaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 41 Kutupa hande toopi pa nane mea wimikime. Yesumaęž‰ handaęž‰liao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka pi opu hale ekinaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alome.  
\v 42 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ aloeki opu hale ekitaęž‰ handolopate pa do haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaaleeki handaęž‰ hone tulaenaęž‰yeke neke paęž‰taęž‰ do pi alome leekeme.  
\v 43 Yesumaęž‰ koto laa anekemaęž‰ wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Laęž‰satesio. Hama epoe leekeme.  
\v 44 Hande homeeke halitaęž‰ kiki anke leke popeleke ipikaęž‰ daumaęž‰ ambula wimiki tupaęž‰ tiao hama epeekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dau leisi mea bao epenaęž‰ tapaape leekeme.   
\s1 Yesu lulu pimiki ekinaęž‰ potaęž‰ weimikieki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰1-5, Maka 14ęž‰1-2, Luku 22ęž‰1-2)  
\p
\v 45 Meti handolo pemeke Diu wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ piekeeki handaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekeme.  
\v 46 Kutu pimikipate mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki lolo pemekeme.  
\v 47 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki make mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make mo KaĚ±leĚ±sete tapake ameĚ±leĚ± mombaęž‰lalo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eki pumanaęž‰pe. Do hande halimaęž‰ wele wotu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 48 Pa pinaęž‰ paomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalimikie. Kutupa make mo Lomaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ nikaęž‰ tembolo da make nikaęž‰ tapake make telipinaęž‰ hoeyaalimikie lemekeme.   
\p
\v 49 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali Kaiyaęž‰pasitaęž‰ koto bapinaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali hataęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handelememe.  
\v 50 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ epekeeki ipilieke. Kutupa nikaęž‰ tapake paeyao hoeyaapeke na yelieke. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe leekeme.  
\v 51 Do leeke ekitaęž‰ Kaiyaęž‰pasimaęž‰ kone pa na leke koto bapinaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali hataęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ homolo piekeeki la halolo hataęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 52 Kutupa make mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ homeke na homeke mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ weki wandikitaęž‰ pa hataęž‰ pepi pea haenaęž‰ kone paeyao handaęž‰ mea homeke tapake kone apaęž‰tao haenaęž‰yeke Yesu homolo paęž‰laęž‰eki la halolo hataęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 53 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰ kini pea Yesu lulu peleme potaęž‰ weimikime.  
\v 54 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pominolo hataęž‰ peneme yao na pomiekepate Diudia nane minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke da Ipoteimi da paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.   
\p
\v 55 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke nate tunkulieke handaa papate da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ne aĚ±iĚ± na pambeke haenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ loke wamo puluekemaęž‰ oli Diutuseleme da nane pemekeme.  
\v 56 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu weitolo hataęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pu alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Eki hone witelemepe. Do hande ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na ipilieke hone witolomaęž‰pate eki hone witelemepe la leekeme.   
\p
\v 57 Kotaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ Yesu halaęž‰eki handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minomonoyeke niki aęž‰pa la kiaęž‰paęž‰peke lemekeme.   
\c 12  
\s1 Bedani da paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ mo nada senisi holaeyekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰6-13, Maka 14ęž‰3-9)  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ nate yunki mindiki hataęž‰ pa winaęž‰ kone Yesutaęž‰ mo Bedani da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Hande Yesumaęž‰ paa mea tiaeyeke hali Laęž‰satesi ipikaęž‰ dae.  
\v 2 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ ne pambaemekeme. Laęž‰satesitaęž‰ teipolonaęž‰ Yesu yaapo mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ Madamaęž‰ hande ne pane pea hale hale piekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa Metimaęž‰ mo nada senisi seliapotaęž‰ yenki tieke ale kone mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ makataęž‰ kilo pa hapo siki tupaęž‰ meataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ anke paęž‰taęž‰ holaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ itikimaęž‰ honiaeyekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ mo senisi totopomaęž‰taęž‰ mo da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ totopo yuyu wia wiekeme.  
\v 4 Mo disaipolo hali homeke Isekatioti hali Diudasitaęž‰ hande Yesu aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo pieke hali ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\v 5 Do senisitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambenaęž‰ laataęž‰ 60 kina meaataęž‰ nate hali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ na teli teli peaemeke ekitaęž‰ ekipeke pimipe leekeme.  
\v 6 Do leeke pitaęž‰ nate hali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo na leke pake hali hataęž‰ leekeme. Mani pausataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ miniki hataęž‰ mea pomiekepate ipikaęž‰ hone wia yokaęž‰ meaęž‰tiki piekeme.  
\v 7 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi na lapeke. Ipikaęž‰ wia halaęž‰eki pa miniki haenaęž‰ IĚ± toko hoiyulu peleme natenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Natehali wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao halo pelemepate IĚ±taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± na hao halumeke leekeme.   
\s1 Laęž‰satesi lulu pimiki potaęž‰ weimikieki  
\p
\v 9 Diu wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Bedani da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halaęž‰me lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme. Yesu homeke handuluekemaęž‰ na pekepate hande Yesumaęž‰ lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa mea tiaeyeke hali Laęž‰satesi make handuluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.  
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Laęž‰satesi make lulu pimiki potaęž‰ weimikime.  
\v 11 Diu haliweki wopumaęž‰ Laęž‰satesi paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ you haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemeke ekinaęž‰ pimikime.   
\s1 Taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Diutuseleme nane pemekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰1-11, Maka 11ęž‰1-11, Luku 19ęž‰28-40)  
\p
\v 12 Da kaęž‰laęž‰peeketaęž‰ hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke dinaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ mombaęž‰la haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane ipulaęž‰me lemekeeki opimikime.  
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ dopemaęž‰ handeke ti palekemanu tondaęž‰paęž‰ mepi pea mina Yesu mandaęž‰hande puluekemaęž‰ wi laęž‰tiki pulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laapaęž‰pe.  
\q1 Tekehalinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\q1 Ipikitaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie la lemekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Yesumaęž‰ donki maęž‰naęž‰ handaęž‰ wiataęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ hoki manda pitiekeme. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa   
\q1
\v 15 Saioni dataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Handaęž‰e. Nakaęž‰ kini hali koto ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Donki maęž‰naęž‰ siki ipikaęž‰ hoki manda pitaęž‰ koto ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ koto hau pieke pitaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ hone na wimikipate pa wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu paa tiao oli ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± piki kapu tieke mulu pieke haenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ dupiki pi wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ kone yaeyekeeki hone wimikime.   
\p
\v 17 Laęž‰satesi lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ wi la paa mea tiaeyeke pitaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto pieke ekitaęž‰ hande wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ la halemekeme.  
\v 18 Koto wele wopu pieke ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opuataęž‰ Yesu mandaęž‰hande pulu pemekeme.  
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ane laęž‰ mone laęž‰ pu alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Handelemepe. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Handaęž‰pe. Wandaęž‰hali paeyaęž‰ tapao ipiki teliaęž‰ mea pulimime lemekeme.   
\s1 Mandane Kitiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu weimikieki  
\p
\v 20 Mo hande ne pambemeke pitaęž‰ Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pulu pemeke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ mandane Kitiki wandaęž‰hali make pemekeme.  
\v 21 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke da Betesaida da hao epeeke hali Pilipi paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu handulumeke hone witolomaęž‰me lemekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Pilipimaęž‰ Aęž‰ndutu paęž‰taęž‰ pua laataęž‰ Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu lolo pepekeme.  
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± piki kapu tieke mulu paęž‰laęž‰ di ame ipulaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Kuni wae alesiki homeketaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ na opaęž‰ pa lopa na homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa u pelia halieke. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ opa kiliki wotu aęž‰elieke.  
\v 25 Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone hone wotu wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ alupilieke. Hali epimaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone hone wopu na wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki mea miniki hataęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halo paęž‰laęž‰eki kone yelieke.  
\v 26 Hali epimaęž‰ yaka e pokaaluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ya hoki nane teliaęž‰ mea epenaęž‰e. Yaka e pokaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ IĚ± halo alenaęž‰ kone diki mandakenaęž‰ halupekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Yaka e pokaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ koto halinaęž‰ biki tieke winaęž‰ lelieke leekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homolo pieke ekinaęž‰ pi leekeeki  
\p
\v 27 Ametaęž‰ ya puki tandamaęž‰ homolome hataęž‰ eki pi lonope. Doeki lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Apaęž‰o. Hande IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ di na epenaęž‰ lapeke lonope. Diaęž‰me. Koto tanda tandamaęž‰ homolo polo di muluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me.  
\v 28 Apaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ biki tieke winaęž‰ lapeke leekeme. Koto la haenaęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ laęž‰niaeyeke pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka bikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ tieke winaęž‰ lolopate paa maęž‰ndaęž‰ alo peao tieke winaęž‰ lolueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ pambulu bao haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opua alotaęž‰ Tutu liaęž‰me lemekeme. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Enisolo halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alopate leaęž‰me lemekepate  
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oli laęž‰niaeyaęž‰ pitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ diaęž‰me. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ laęž‰niaaso leaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Ametaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ di ipulaęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ tumiki halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ yoka mea lopaalieke.  
\v 32 Kutupa IĚ±taęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hano IĚ± mea aęž‰meiyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ yolaęž‰ mulueke leekeme.  
\v 33 Koto leeke ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homolo piekeeki la halolo leekeme.  
\v 34 Koto leeketaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo Lo Pi manumaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ doeki opumaęž‰me. Ketisotaęž‰ hao halieke alaęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke mea aęž‰meiyalieke ale ekitaęž‰ ekipape. Mo hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ epiyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe lemekeme.   
\p
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hosiki halimikie. Timbaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki mea tombuaamaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ kone puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Timbaęž‰ laęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pulaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ Dotaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ pulupe lelieke.  
\v 36 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ hataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wekiwandiki leke haminaęž‰yeke paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ kone hone tulaapaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\s1 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaemekeeki  
\p Yesumaęž‰ koto pi laataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao puataęž‰ panka halo peekeme.  
\v 37 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ kone wele wotu pieke ekimanu mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handaa kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaemekeme.  
\v 38 Mo hande potopede hali Aisayamaęž‰ leeke ekimanu yaenaęž‰yeke piekeme. Dupa  
\q1 Tekehalio. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ la halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epimaęž‰ opimipe.  
\q1 Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele pieke ekitaęž‰ epi paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰pe laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone tulaapeke na yeeke ekinaęž‰ Aisayamaęž‰ leekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa   
\q1
\v 40 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke holu peaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukitaęž‰ takaęž‰laęž‰pa pua hataęž‰taęž‰ toopi leke winaęž‰ leekeme.  
\q1 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaamaęž‰naęž‰ make ikaęž‰ puki toolumaęž‰ hone wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ puaęž‰me.  
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ iki wamo peaanoyeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na laęž‰kaęž‰la haenaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 41 Koto leeke pitaęž‰ Aisayamaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke mea hayekeeki handeeke ekinaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰eki hone witolo hataęž‰ leekeme.   
\p
\v 42 Kutu pimikipate mo Diu you haliweki wopumaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekepate mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pieke handaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ulaęž‰eki yokaamaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki peneme yao na lemekeme.  
\v 43 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laenaęž‰ hone na wiki kenke haliwekimaęž‰ laenaęž‰ hone wopu wimikime.   
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ leeke pi manumaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 44 Yesumaęž‰ pi anekemaęž‰ alo alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone na tulaake IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ make pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 45 Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali make handaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 46 IĚ±taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki tupaęž‰ aęž‰pa halome. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pambaęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na haenaęž‰yeke epoaęž‰me.  
\v 47 Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opua na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto hali yaapo IĚ±maęž‰ pi yokaalu na pulueke. Kenke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ na epeke iki mea daęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me.  
\v 48 Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± kiaaso hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi na opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki yaapo pi yokaalu pilieke. Do IĚ±maęž‰ aloeki manumaęž‰ kone paelie natenaęž‰ ipiki yaapo pi yokaalu pilieke.  
\v 49 IĚ±maęž‰ ya hone wia na loaęž‰me. IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ lolo puaęž‰ ekimanu paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lapeke leeke handaa puaęž‰me.  
\v 50 Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ du peaęž‰peke la alaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰eki kone peaasaęž‰ekie hone witolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ lapeke leaęž‰ pi kone alome leekeme.   
\c 13  
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekinaęž‰ anke tandaęž‰paeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ do kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao Ateke paęž‰taęž‰ polo pieke di ambaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰laęž‰me hone wiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haemeke ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo hao paeyaalo pulu hataęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeekeme.   
\p
\v 2 Welealo nane Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ne no pitimikime. Isekatioti hali Saimononaęž‰ eiyeke Diudasimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo pieke honetaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ mea wiaeyekeme.  
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ hande ipikaęž‰ Atekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeeki make ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo hao aęž‰pa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polo piekeeki make hone wiekeme.  
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo teipolo minaęž‰paęž‰lao tiaotaęž‰ manda pambaeyeke dau holaęž‰ mea wiaataęž‰ dawelo mea tonkaeyekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupataęž‰ maęž‰tiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikali holaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki ikaęž‰ ankemanu homeke paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pea tandaęž‰paęž‰tiki pea hande tonkaeyeke dawelomaęž‰ honiaęž‰tiki piekeme.  
\v 6 Kutupataęž‰ Saimono Pida pitieke paęž‰taęž‰ peekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehali nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ya anke tandaęž‰puluekemaęž‰ pi leekeme.  
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ame do pitolo ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na witelepate wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ hone wilipikie leekeme.  
\v 8 Pidamaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka anke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ tandaęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke na tandaęž‰poaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaka disaipolo hali hapeke na yelieke leekeme.  
\v 9 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Kotaęž‰ yaka anke homeke diaęž‰me laataęž‰ Yaka kiki you tonkaęž‰naęž‰ tandaęž‰pae leekeme.  
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke paeyao tenke lao ikali peiya hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke paeyao wamo pea haluekemaęž‰ ikali pa na peiyiki ipikaęž‰ anke homeke pa tandaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Iki paeyao ambaęž‰ wamo pea halemepate hali homeketaęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo pieke hali ambaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ koto pi leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Iki paeyao ambaęž‰ wamo pea halemepate hali homeke diaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ anke tandaęž‰pa paeyeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau paa mea pambao ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ pitieke teipolo paęž‰taęž‰ paa pua tepiao pitiekeme. Mo haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo  
\v 13 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± biki yaapo alo hataęž‰ Disa make Tekehali make aleme ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰piki pi alememe. IĚ±taęž‰ koto polome.  
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Tekehali make Disa make hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ anke tandepoaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ ankemanu tandaęž‰paęž‰ alualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo.  
\v 15 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ peaowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make puemenaęž‰yeke walaęž‰ tiaaso puaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e teke hali ankulapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa pi lolo penaęž‰ tapaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ make ipiki tapaasaęž‰ hali kone ankulaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 17 Do walo ekitaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ kone taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie.   
\p
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ na alome. Ya talopu molo haliweki ambaęž‰ handoaęž‰me. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ yaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me dupae. Dikaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne nopaęž‰ halimaęž‰ kone IĚ± yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkula halaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Dupiki hau aĚ±iĚ± na piki haenaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ ame do kone la kitolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ koto hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yaka halo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ halome. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone wilimikie.  
\v 20 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ tapaaso hali handaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± make handaęž‰ minolo pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupataęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali kone handaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo pulu piekeeki laęž‰ wiekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰20-25, Maka 14ęž‰17-21, Luku 22ęž‰21-23)  
\p
\v 21 Kotoeki laa Yesumaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolo hataęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Iki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombelieke leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Mo disaipolo haliweki pa penkili pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ane handaęž‰ mone handaęž‰ pitolo epi paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰pe hone wimikime.  
\v 23 Disaipolo hali homeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ puki pieke halitaęž‰ Yesu yaapo lopu laęž‰ alu pea pitiekeme.  
\v 24 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ so laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Epi paęž‰taęž‰ alepe. Lotaęž‰ pie leekeme.  
\v 25 Koto leeke handaa mo disaipolo halimaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰pea pitaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Epi paęž‰taęž‰ alepe leekeme.  
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do palaowataęž‰ kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ tenke lao halue halitaęž‰ koto halie leekeme. Kotoeki la ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ palaowa meataęž‰ tenke lao mo Isekatioti hali Saimono ipikaęž‰ eiyeke Diudasi paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.  
\v 27 Diudasimaęž‰ hande palaowa mieke pitaęž‰ kone Sadanitaęž‰ ipiki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu epeekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ pulu peleeki aĚ±iĚ± pua peaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰ Diudasi paęž‰taęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ mo teipolo paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki haliweki homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hone na wimikime.  
\v 29 Mandane disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Diudasimaęž‰ mo mani pausa handeteke hayeke ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hambolo penaęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰pe o natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ halo pu la tapaeyaęž‰pe hone wimikime.  
\v 30 Diudasimaęž‰ mo palaowa meataęž‰ kuta kone hama opolu bao peekeme. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pambeekeme.   
\s1 Mo panake pi ulaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 31 Diudasi peeke hoki nane Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki milieke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ handulumeke.  
\v 32 Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ peaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki peaalieke. Kutupa kuta kone peaalieke.  
\v 33 Yaka weki wandikio. Iki ameĚ±leĚ± halo polomaęž‰patetaęž‰ hosiki halueke. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± weilimikipate pa ambaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make alome. IĚ± polue da nanetaęž‰ iki aęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me la leekeme.  
\v 34 Ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ panake pi ulaęž‰eki laęž‰ wiaasome dupa. Ikaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homaalu alu pea hapaęž‰peke. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homao tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homaalu alu peaęž‰paęž‰peke laa  
\v 35 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaalu alu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yaka disaipolo haliweki haleme ekitaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ handilimikie la leekeme.   
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki hoeyaaso pulu pieke ekitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰31-35, Maka 14ęž‰27-31, Luku 22ęž‰31-34)  
\p
\v 36 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neketaęž‰ hane poluekemaęž‰ alepe leeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± polue nanetaęž‰ ame IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea aęž‰paęž‰peke na yolo paęž‰laęž‰pate wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ teliaęž‰ mea ipilipikie leekeme.  
\v 37 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Ekipeke neke na teliaęž‰ mea ipilipiki la alepe laataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yaka daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki homaoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make anaęž‰ pilieke laa leekepate  
\v 38 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ homoluekemaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alepe laa neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi do alome. Mo hali kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ eĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na leke haenaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto teponaęž‰ IĚ± Yesu na handolome laa lelipikie leekeme.   
\c 14  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pulaęž‰ potaęž‰e  
\p
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pomomaęž‰ na homeke hone eleke eleke na wiki hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hone tulao hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 2 Yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ da pandaęž‰ eleke eleke wotu ulaęž‰me. Kutupa IĚ± puataęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰pa halo peleme alenaęž‰ wamo peaalo pulaęž‰me. Do aloeki na wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ la kulu puaęž‰me laa leekeme.  
\v 3 Kutupa IĚ± pua ikaęž‰ halo peleme alenaęž‰ wamo peaotaęž‰ IĚ± halo alenaęž‰ mandake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa haminaęž‰yeke IĚ± paa aęž‰pa iki aęž‰pa handaęž‰ mulueke.  
\v 4 Kutupa IĚ± pulueeki make potaęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handelememe laa leekeme.  
\v 5 Tomasimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neke polo pele ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ na handolomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ ekipa handomonope laa leeke handaa  
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hande potaęž‰e. IĚ± otaęž‰ekie laa IĚ±taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ekie. Hali epimaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ homeke epenaęž‰e leekeme.  
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ make handilimikie. Ametaęž‰ ipiki handolo pelemeeki ametaęž‰ kini pitelememe laa ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ handelememe la leekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Pilipimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Nakaęž‰ Apaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰e. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke leekeme.  
\v 9 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Pilipio. Iki paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± nate wopu haowaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone na wia alepe. IĚ± handiliaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ make handilieke laa ekipeke handa nakaęž‰ Apaęž‰ walaęž‰e alepe.  
\v 10 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo halaęž‰eki make IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka Apaęž‰ yaapo haloeki make hone na witelepe leekeme. Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ ya hone wia na loaęž‰me laa hande IĚ± yaapo halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰eki pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ yaapo halo ekinaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa do aloeki na opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hande puaęž‰ ekimanu hone witolo hataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hapaęž‰peke laa leekeme.  
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome laa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pitoloeki manutaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pilieke. Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± polue ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pitolo ekimanu kone mo halimaęž‰ ankulao hau tiekemanu pilieke leekeme.  
\v 13 Kutupa alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaka bikimaęž‰ honke alo hataęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande Atekemaęž‰ hande Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ peaalueke leekeme.  
\v 14 Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaka biki alo hataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honke lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ peaalueke leekeme.   
\s1 Mo hande laęž‰ wieke Holi Sipitidi  
\p
\v 15 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homekenaęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pilimikie.  
\v 16-17 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ honke loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao haenaęž‰ leliaęž‰ mo Tambaęž‰ Mu Halo Paęž‰laęž‰ Hali kilieke. Ipikitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki pu halaęž‰ Epeke Temoko konee. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki na handolo hataęž‰ make hone na witolo hataęž‰ make ipiki handaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yolo paęž‰laęž‰pate iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake hataęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki handelememe.   
\p
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pa honumake haminaęž‰ na lolueke. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulueke laa  
\v 19 hosiki hao kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ IĚ± pa na handolo pelemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wetepe IĚ± handilimikie. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± daęž‰taęž‰ halo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki make daęž‰taęž‰ halimikie.  
\v 20 Kutupa koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haloeki make ikitaęž‰ IĚ± tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ halemeeki make iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± haloeki make handilimikie laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 21 Hali epimaęž‰ yaka pi ulu ekimanu opua piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homilie halitaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homilieke. Kutupa make IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ IĚ± halo ekitaęž‰ peneme yaalueke laa leekeme.  
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ koto leeke handaataęž‰ Diudasi hande Isekatioti hali Diudasi paęž‰taęž‰ na loaęž‰maęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Ekipa kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ na handenaęž‰ leke niki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke peneme yao walipikipe leekeme.  
\v 23 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opua pilieke. Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ koto hali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homilieke. Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰ dikitaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± hao halumeke.  
\v 24 Pate hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi manutaęž‰ na opilieke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do opueleme pitaęž‰ yakaeki diaęž‰me pa IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 25 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± halo dinaęž‰taęž‰ do pimanu la kitolome.  
\v 26 Kutu pitolopate hande iki Tambaęž‰ Mulu paęž‰laęž‰ Hali yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ yaka bikinaęž‰ tapaalo paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi kone alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ walieke. Kutupa make IĚ±maęž‰ hande iki paęž‰taęž‰ walo ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone uemenaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone u tiaalieke.   
\p
\v 27 IĚ±maęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pulupate puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa winaęž‰ laa pulume. Yaka puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitolome. Kutupa mo kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ pa na kitolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ hone eleke eleke na wiki paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme.  
\v 28 IĚ±maęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao polueke laa loaęž‰patetaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulueke laa loaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opimime. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ mo yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± pulume loaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo pimime. Pa ekipeke yaka Apaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ankulao halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 29 Do alo ekimanu aĚ±iĚ± na epeke haenaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolome. Pa ekipeke otaęž‰ yaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaalimikie leekeme.  
\v 30 Do kenkenaęž‰ you hali epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi wotu na lolueke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 31 Pa IĚ±maęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo ekitaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ doeki peaęž‰peke leaęž‰ haumanu paeyao pu halome laataęž‰ Tiao do paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pomanaęž‰e laa leekeme.   
\c 15  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ waini pu tekee  
\p
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ waini pu tekee. Kutupa yaka Apaęž‰taęž‰ mo waini pu enaęž‰ teke halie.  
\v 2 Yaka paleke mandane ekimaęž‰ kiliki na aęž‰eyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto paleketaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ poka mea baalieke. Kutupa mo mandane kiliki aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ paleke manutaęž‰ wamo peaaso hataęž‰ kiliki wopu aęž‰enaęž‰yeke yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ pokaęž‰ mepi pilieke.  
\v 3 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ loaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ wamo paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 4 Ikitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ halueke. Mo hande paleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ na tunaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone kiliki aęž‰eyaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Iki make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone kiliki na aęž‰elieke.   
\p
\v 5 IĚ±taęž‰ waini pu tekee. Ikitaęž‰ palekemanue. Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ipiki yaapo hataęž‰ kiliki wotu aęž‰elieke. Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± na hake hataęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hau homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na pilimikie.  
\v 6 Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo hande hapuaęž‰laęž‰ palekemaęž‰ handilieke. Kutupa mo hapuaęž‰laęž‰ paleke manutaęž‰ amu pea ti uleke paęž‰taęž‰ lopaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ timaęž‰ telieke.  
\v 7 Ikitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi lolo ekimanu miniki hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ honke lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ milimikie.  
\v 8 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kiliki wotu aęž‰eteleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ biki tieke wiaasememe. Kutu piteleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yaka disaipolo haliweki halimikie leekeme.  
\v 9 Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ homoloeki paęž‰taęž‰ hao hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 10 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua peataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halo tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make yaka pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ homoloeki paęž‰taęž‰ halimikie laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Do alomaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ yaka taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homoloeki iki paęž‰taęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki tumba pitinaęž‰yeke iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome.  
\v 12 Yaka pi witolo ekitaęž‰ dupae. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homaalualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 13 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke tambaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone alu paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutupiki pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ankulapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ dupaęž‰paęž‰ aloeki opua pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yaka yankeke titi halimikie.  
\v 15 Pa e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke halimaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa e pokaaseme haliwekio pi na lolueke. Pa ekipeke yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kitaęž‰laęž‰ pi paeyao iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolo ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ yaka yankeke titio alome laa leekeme.  
\v 16 IĚ±taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na mea haenaęž‰ lelemepate pa ikitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ talopu meaataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pua hande u halo paęž‰laęž‰ napeke aęž‰eyaminaęž‰yeke mea haenaęž‰ lolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaka biki alo hataęž‰ honke lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ kilieke.  
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi witoloeki dupae. Ikaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homaalu alu pea hapaęž‰peke laa leekeme.   
\s1 Kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lilaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 18 Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lilimieki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 19 Ikitaęž‰ do kenke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ tapakee laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo pimime. Kutu pulu pimipate IĚ±maęž‰ iki talopu mea haminaęž‰ lolo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo kenkenaęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± na halememe. Koto peleme ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ litelememe.  
\v 20 IĚ±maęž‰ alo pinaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. E pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ teke hali na ankulalieke laa loaęž‰me. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰ndaęž‰ lilimikie. IĚ±maęž‰ walolo pi opueleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ walo pelemeeki make opilimikie.  
\v 21 Ikitaęž‰ yakaeki halemeke handaa do haumanu paeyao iki paęž‰taęž‰ pilimikie. Kutupa make IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali na handolo hataęž‰ pilimikie.  
\v 22 IĚ±maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰pa loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peneme na yaalo pimime. Kutu pulu piaęž‰patetaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekinaęž‰ hombo pealuekemaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 23 Hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 24 Ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na pieke ekimanu IĚ±maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± na puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ peneme na yaalo piaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰eki handaa kone yaka Apaęž‰ diki paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pu halememe.  
\v 25 Kutu pitelemepate ikaęž‰ Lo Pi manunaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ yaaluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Dupae. Pa hameke kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pimime.   
\p
\v 26 Kutu pitelemepate mo Tambaęž‰ Mu Halaęž‰ Hali ipilieke. Ipikitaęž‰ Ateke yaapo halaęž‰ hali kone IĚ±maęž‰ tapaalueke. Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pu halaęž‰ Temokoe. Ipikitaęž‰ Ateke paęž‰taęž‰ hao ipilieke. Kutupa yaka pi laęž‰ mea halawaasaęž‰ wekitisi hali halieke.  
\v 27 Kutupa iki make ambaęž‰ kone IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haleme ekinaęž‰ yaka pi lawaaseme wekitisi haliweki halimikie.   
\c 16  
\p
\v 1 Ikaęž‰ hone tulao halemeeki wetepenaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalo peleme tupaęž‰ do pimanu paeyao iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolome.  
\v 2 Mo hande pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰manu iki poemenaęž‰yeke iki yokilimikie. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki litolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰me laa hone wilimikie.  
\v 3 Yaka Apaęž‰ diki na handeleme ekinaęž‰ koto haumanu pilimikie.  
\v 4 Kutu pulu pelemepate koto haumanu pulu peleme nate epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande IĚ±maęž‰ loaęž‰ ekimanu ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone uemenaęž‰yeke do pimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kitolome.  
\s1 Mo Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p IĚ±taęž‰ panake paęž‰taęž‰ kone iki ameĚ±leĚ± haowaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do pimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ na la kuaęž‰pate  
\v 5 Pa ametaęž‰ IĚ± tapaalaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ paa pulume laa alo ekitaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hane pulipe la make na lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa ametaęž‰ do hande pimanu la kuaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ puki tetomaęž‰ homelememe.  
\v 7 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do otaęž‰ pi alome. IĚ±maęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao polue ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epekeekie laa do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. IĚ± na poaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande Tambaęž‰ Mulu Paęž‰laęž‰ Halitaęž‰ na ipilieke. Kutupa IĚ± poaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hande hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mea tapaalueke.  
\v 8 Kutupa aęž‰paataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ make tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ make pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ hone u hoeyaasekeeki peneme yao walieke.  
\v 9 Mo hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hone u hoeyaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaaseme ekinaęž‰ pitelememe.  
\v 10 Mo tiki tiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hone u hoeyaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polo polopate IĚ± paa na handolo peleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Mo pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hone u hoeyaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ you halitaęž‰ pi yokaalu peataęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Mandane pi eleke eleke iki paęž‰taęž‰ lolo polopate pomomaęž‰ weleke taapaęž‰naęž‰ ame do na la kulueke.  
\v 13 Kutu polopate wetepe hande otaęž‰ pi la walaęž‰laęž‰ Temoko epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu paeyao opuemenaęž‰ iki tikitiki yao hatuku pelieke. Ipikaęž‰ hone wia na leke eki pi opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto pi kone la kilieke. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ pulu peleme ekimanu make la kilieke.  
\v 14 Yaka pi kone opua iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka biki mea aęž‰meiyalieke.  
\v 15 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ wia halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ya ekie. Koto polo ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Temoko paęž‰taęž‰ halolo ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ meaataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kilieke loaęž‰me.   
\s1 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki yelieke  
\p
\v 16 Hosiki hao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paa na handaataęž‰ pa hosiki hao hao pea IĚ± paa handilimikie.  
\v 17 Mandane disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi la alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Do alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ eki epinaęž‰ alaęž‰pe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hosiki hao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paa na handaataęž‰ kutupa pa hosiki hao hao pea IĚ± paa handilimikie leaęž‰me. Kutupa make yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ polo polo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me leaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 18 Kutupa ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pu alu alu pitolo alotaęž‰ Hande hosiki hao leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ eki epinaęž‰ leaęž‰pe laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ pi teketaęž‰ niki hone na witolomaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pulu pimikieki hone wia iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hosiki hao ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paa na handaataęž‰ pa hosiki hao hao pea IĚ± paa handilimikie loaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Ikaęž‰ kone ane laęž‰ mone laęž‰ pitelemepe.  
\v 20 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ eĚ± lolo pelemepate kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie. Ikitaęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homolo pelemepate kutupulu pelemeeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa halimikie.  
\v 21 Wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰taęž‰ weki loke lomba hao hoki neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki mulu paęž‰laęž‰ di ipulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tandamaęž‰ homiliepate pa mo hande weki miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo wekitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ mendiaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tanda miaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰laalieke.  
\v 22 Iki make koto tupaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ ame kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homelemepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paa handulueke. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie. Kutupa koto ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo peleme ekitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yokuluekemaęž‰ na bepolalieke.   
\p
\v 23 Koto di epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ honke na lelimikie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hande yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka bikinaęž‰ honke lolo peleme ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kilieke.  
\v 24 Ambaęž‰ make ame do make yaka bikinaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ honke na lememe. Honke lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ milimikie. Kutupa make ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo peleme ekitaęž‰ tumbulu bao halieke.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu ambaęž‰ bepolalaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 25 Do pitaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰pate wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na leke pa yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ peneme yao iki paęž‰taęž‰ lolueke.  
\v 26 Koto di epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yaka biki laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke lelimikie. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa na lolueke. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰eki honke lalueke pi na lolueke.  
\v 27 Pa ekipeke yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homa IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo hao epoloeki opimiki handaa pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 28 IĚ±taęž‰ hande yaka Apaęž‰ yaapo hao do kenkenaęž‰ aęž‰pa hao ametaęž‰ do kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ polueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 29 Koto leekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa na leke peneme yao aleme ekinaęž‰  
\v 30 ametaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolomaęž‰me laa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la lotaęž‰ pinaęž‰yeke na handeteke haleme. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hau paeyao handeleme. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo hao epele ekitaęž‰ opolomaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ hone tulaasemepe.  
\v 32 Opuaęž‰pe. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate ambaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ iki paeyao tankulu paalu pea taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ lo ikaęž‰ da ninaęž‰ kone polo pelemepate IĚ± ya honumake siki pa halueke. Kutu pulu pelemepate IĚ±taęž‰ honumake na hake yaka Apaęž‰ yaapo mandakenaęž‰ halupeke.  
\v 33 Do la kitolo pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ puki lopaęž‰niao haminaęž‰yeke la loaęž‰me. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tanda kulu pelemepate honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke. Do kenkenaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ bepolao ulume leekeme.   
\c 17  
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ koto pimanu laataęž‰ oli ya nane handaęž‰liao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Hande di ambaęž‰ epaęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ wekimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyaenaęž‰yeke nakaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ biki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyapeke.  
\v 2 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ you haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ halo pele wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰tao hao haenaęž‰yeke lele ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Neke homeke otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ haleeki make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ tapaale hali Yesu Ketiso halaęž‰eki make telipinaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰ekie.  
\v 4 Neke tieke haleeki do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ walaataęž‰ kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wale e make poko paeyaowaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Apaęž‰o. Ambaęž‰ do kenke aĚ±iĚ± na wepiki hataęž‰ neke yaapo hataęž‰ muaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± piki kapu tieketaęž‰ kotoeki kone ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hano kie.   
\p
\v 6 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mea ki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ neke haleeki peneme yaowaęž‰me. Koto haliwekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ eki haenaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mea kime. Kutupa nakaęž‰ pi make opimime.  
\v 7 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ki alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ kone muaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ame handelememe.  
\v 8 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la ki pimanu paeyaęž‰ tapao iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰me. Kutu puaęž‰peke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opua mimime. IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo epoloeki make otaęž‰ekie laa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaeeki make opitelememe.   
\p
\v 9 Do haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ yeni pitolome. Kenke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ yeni na piki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ki haliwekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰eki kone koto haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ yeni pitolome.  
\v 10 Yaka wia halo alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ ekie. Kutupa nakaęž‰ wia hale alemanu paeyao make yaka ekie. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ koto haliwekimaęž‰ yaka biki mea aęž‰meiyalememe.  
\v 11 Ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ pa na hake neke paęž‰taęž‰ epolo polopate do haliwekitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ pa ha pelia halimikie. Yako piki Apaęž‰o. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ki bikitaęž‰ koto bikinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ iki handeteke haenaęž‰ lapeke. Dikitaęž‰ homeke kone halopaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki make homeke tupaęž‰ haenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 12 IĚ±taęž‰ do haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ki bikitaęž‰ koto bikinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ kone iki wotu handeteke haowaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki handeteke haowaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na alu piaęž‰pate pa mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki yaenaęž‰yeke hande alu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ hali homekee.  
\v 13 Ametaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ epolo polopate do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do haliwekimaęž‰ yaka taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki mea tumbao haenaęž‰yeke do pimanu alome.  
\v 14 Nakaęž‰ pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ la haloaęž‰me. Koto polo ekinaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pu halememe. IĚ±taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰eki na halo tupaęž‰ koto haliweki make do kenkenaęž‰eki na haleme ekinaęž‰ pitelememe.  
\v 15 IĚ±maęž‰ do honke alo ekitaęž‰ do haliweki kenke paęž‰taęž‰ na haenaęž‰ yokaęž‰ muelenaęž‰ laa na loaęž‰patetaęž‰ hande Hoke Halimaęž‰ iki hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halenaęž‰yeke honke alome.  
\v 16 IĚ±taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰eki na halo tupaęž‰ iki make do kenkenaęž‰eki na halememe.  
\v 17 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lele ekimaęž‰ do haliwekitaęž‰ yakopiki haliweki haenaęž‰ lapeke. Nakaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekie.  
\v 18 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± do kenkenaęž‰ tapae tupaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do haliweki kenke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tapaowaęž‰me.  
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰ do haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ IĚ± ya kone neke paęž‰taęž‰ kitolome. Kutupa do haliweki make otaęž‰ nakaęž‰eki haenaęž‰yeke pitolome.   
\p
\v 20 IĚ±maęž‰ do haliweki homeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ yeni na piki ikaęž‰ pua walo pelemeeki opua IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halo peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make hone witolo hataęž‰ yeni pitolome.  
\v 21 Paeyaotaęž‰ homekeeki haenaęž‰yeke yeni pitolome. Apaęž‰o. Neketaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo haleeki make IĚ± neke yaapo haloeki make iki make koto tupaęž‰ diki ameĚ±leĚ± haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaaleeki hone winaęž‰yeke ikitaęž‰ homekeeki haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 22 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hande ki biki tieketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ haloaęž‰me. Diki homeke kone halopaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki make homekeeki haenaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me.  
\v 23 IĚ±taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ haloeki make neketaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ haleeki make ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homekeeki haenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaaleeki make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homele tupaęž‰ do haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ koto homeke pukimaęž‰ homeleeki make hone winaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 24 Apaęž‰o. Do haliwekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ keleme. Koto pele ekinaęž‰ IĚ± halo alenaęž‰ iki make koto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ yaka paĚ±aĚ± piki biki tieke moloeki handenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto biki tieketaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ keleekie. Do kenke aĚ±iĚ± na wepieke dinaęž‰ kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homele ekinaęž‰ keleme.  
\v 25 Tiki tiki piki Apaęž‰o. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ neke na handelemepate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke handolome. Kutupa do haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tapaale ekitaęž‰ handelememe.  
\v 26 Nakaęž‰ hale ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰pate pa walaęž‰tiki pulueke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homele ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make pitinaęž‰yeke kutupa IĚ± make iki paęž‰taęž‰ hanoyeke pulueke.   
\c 18  
\s1 Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimikieki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰47-56, Maka 14ęž‰43-50, Luku 22ęž‰47-53)  
\p
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ koto pi lo paeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pua mo Kidotoni mukiki lombei pupa pemekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± e maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambolo pemekeme.  
\v 2 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki mandaęž‰hande pu hayeke handaataęž‰ kutu pu hayeke ekitaęž‰ hande Yesu aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeeke hali Diudasimaęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ handeekeme.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudasimaęž‰taęž‰ mandane ami haliweki make mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki mo Paęž‰tisi haliweki yaapomaęž‰ tapaemeke tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliweki make hande e paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku peekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ olaęž‰pake make aęž‰ndelimanu make mutia pemekeme.  
\v 4 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epolo pieke hau paeyao hone wia mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pua lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Epi weitelemepe leekeme.   
\p
\v 5 Koto leeke handa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu wei mea epomaęž‰me lemekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto halitaęž‰ IĚ± dotaęž‰ leekeme. Hande Yesu aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeeke hali Diudasitaęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao hayekeme.  
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ Koto halitaęž‰ IĚ± dotaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekitaęž‰ yolaęž‰ pamba kenkenaęž‰ lopemekeme.  
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Epi weitelemepe leekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu weitolomaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±e laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ la kuaęž‰me. IĚ± weitolo lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do haliweki pao penaęž‰ lape leekeme.  
\v 9 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki pi leeke ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki yaenaęž‰yeke leekeme. Dupae. Apaęž‰o. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ki haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke kone na alupiaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 10 Saimono Pidamaęž‰taęž‰ kepete hokulu pankaęž‰niao hayekeeki yolo tia mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ e pokaeyeke hali pokeekepate ipikaęž‰ popeke nane katake tunkulaęž‰ pokeekeme. Mo pokaeyeke halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Maęž‰likusie.  
\v 11 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kepete hokulu pao mea dake paęž‰taęž‰ pankaęž‰niae. Yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰laęž‰ kapo ikalitaęž‰ na noluepe leekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Aęž‰nasinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hayekeeki  
\p
\v 12 Mo ami haliweki ikaęž‰ you hali tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliweki make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minaataęž‰ pumaęž‰ tonkao  
\v 13 Aęž‰nasi paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰laęž‰ hatuku pemekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ koto bapinaęž‰ yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali Kaiyaęž‰pasi ipikaęž‰ meiyeke hayekeme.  
\v 14 Kaiyaęž‰pasitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leeke halie. Wandaęž‰hali paeyao homaamaęž‰naęž‰ hali homeke kone homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ epelieke laa leekeme.   
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki hoeyaeyekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰69-70, Maka 14ęž‰66-68, Luku 22ęž‰55-57)  
\p
\v 15 Saimono Pida make disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ make Yesu teliaęž‰ mea pepekeme. Mo hande disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ hando hatiki pieke handaa ipikitaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ da hama paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± peekeme.  
\v 16 Pidataęž‰ mo potaęž‰ kake hamaęž‰ nane pa hayekeme. Mo disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ hande yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ hando hatiki pieke halimaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la puaataęž‰ mo potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laataęž‰ Pida tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeekeme.  
\v 17 Mo potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke wandikimaęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ do hande halinaęž‰ disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ pate yaęž‰laęž‰me laa leekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Kosaęž‰ pieke handa mo e pokaemeke haliweki make mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliweki make paeyaomaęž‰ punu lankake mombaęž‰lao taęž‰naęž‰ laataęž‰ titipunaęž‰ pambo haemekeme. Pida make ipikaęž‰ loke titipu pinaęž‰ alo mo haliweki haemeke alenaęž‰ pua hayekeme.   
\s1 Mo yeni peao hayeke you halimaęž‰ Yesu lotaęž‰ piekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰59-66, Maka 14ęž‰55-64, Luku 22ęž‰66-71)  
\p
\v 19 Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki haemekeeki make ipikaęž‰ walaęž‰tiki piekeeki make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ walo haowaęž‰me. Kutupa Diu wandaęž‰hali mombolo haleme alenaęž‰ make mo pi hotu haleme da paęž‰taęž‰manu make mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki puaęž‰me. Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na aęž‰mbao loaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Kutu puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ± ekipeke lotaęž‰ pitolo alepe laa IĚ±maęž‰ waloeki opimi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pie. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ hone wia halememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ waloeki opuelenaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pie leekeme.  
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ koto pi leeke handaa mo tembolo da handeteke hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kadapomaęž‰ lia alotaęž‰ Do yeni peao haleme you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso hataęž‰ ekipeke kutupiki pi alepe leekeme.  
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi lo hoeyaowaęž‰eki opikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do haliweki paeyao opinaęž‰ la halaęž‰e laataęž‰ kutupulu pelepate otaęž‰ pi loaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kone pikaęž‰naęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ekipeke lipe leekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ Aęž‰nasimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ tonkao pelia haenaęž‰ kone mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali Kaiyaęž‰pasi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeme.   
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki paa hoeyaeyekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰71-75, Maka 14ęž‰69-72, Luku 22ęž‰58-62)  
\p
\v 25 Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke titipu pinaęž‰ alo koto paęž‰taęž‰ pa ha pelia hayekeme. Kutupu haenaęž‰ mo mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo hande halinaęž‰ disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halepe lemekepate Pidamaęž‰ aęž‰mbaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 26 Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ e pokao hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ katake tunkulaęž‰ pokeeke halinaęž‰ tapake hayeke halimaęž‰ pi alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ mo hande hali ameĚ±leĚ± mo e paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeeki IĚ±maęž‰ na handoaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 27 Pidamaęž‰ Diaęž‰me pi paa alo haenaęž‰ kone mo hali kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ eĚ± leekeme.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Pailedinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hayekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰1-2, Maka 15ęž‰1-5, Luku 23ęž‰1-5)  
\p
\v 28 Kaiyaęž‰pasi hayeke alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Kapomani You halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hatuku mea pemekeme. Da panake kaęž‰laęž‰polo haenaęž‰ mea pemekeme. Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ekinaęž‰ ne pambemekeeki noluekemaęž‰ iki hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ nindi pelemeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ na peke hamaęž‰ nane pa haemekeme.  
\v 29 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane pua iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰ eki hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ samani pulu epemepe leekeme.  
\v 30 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰ ketete na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ na hatuku epolo pumaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 31 Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone hatuku pua ikaęž‰ pi wilimi alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone nikaęž‰ hone wia hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ lia homaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 32 Koto lemeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homolo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone yaaluekemaęž‰ lemekeme.  
\v 33 Pailedimaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la pua hataęž‰ Yesu epenaęž‰ wi laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini hali halepe leekeme.  
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone wia IĚ± lotaęž‰ pitolo alepe o mandane haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ poloeki neke paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 35 Pailedimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Diu hali patemaęž‰ alepe. Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ neke hatuku mea epememe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ eki hau pelepe leekeme.  
\v 36 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka Kilu Tombuao Halo ekitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Yaka Kilu Tombuao Halo ekitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰eki yolutaęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea pomineleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± minaamaęž‰naęž‰ yaka aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaalo pimime. Diaęž‰me. Yaka Kilu Tombuao Halo ekitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰eki diaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 37 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ ipiki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ kini hali yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kini halie ale ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ alee. IĚ±taęž‰ hau homeke puluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me. Mo otaęž‰ pi waluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutu pionoyeke yaka amaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± mendieke do kenkenaęž‰ epoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo otaęž‰ pi opuluekemaęž‰ katake na aęž‰mba haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi alo ekitaęž‰ opu halememe.   
\p
\v 38 Pailedimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ pi alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handoekipe leekeme.  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ homenaęž‰yeke pi leekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰15-31, Maka 15ęž‰6-20, Luku 23ęž‰13-25)  
\p Koto pi laa Pailedimaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane pua mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halimaęž‰ ketete maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na handaęž‰ uaęž‰me laa  
\v 39 kutu puaęž‰pate hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke pitaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pu haleme tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dipula hali homeke pa tapao halome. Koto ekinaęž‰ do Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini hali pa tapawanope leekeme.  
\v 40 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso wi la alualu pea alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Batabasie lemekeme. Mokoto Batabasitaęž‰ hali lu taęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ pa yolaęž‰tiki pomu hayeke halie.   
\c 19  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu meataęž‰ yumbinaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 2 Mo ami haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ tekeke hake pumanu mea panka pea you akaęž‰ wepia ipikaęž‰ younaęž‰ pambaemekeme. Kutupataęž‰ wepiki dau mea dopuao  
\v 3 otaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pea alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini halie laataęž‰ kadapomaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\p
\v 4 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ketete maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na handaęž‰ uaęž‰eki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handoemenaęž‰ do iki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku ipulueke leekeme.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo tekeke hake pu manumaęž‰ wepieke you akaęž‰ pambao mo wepiki dau dopua hamaęž‰ nane peekeme. Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande hali domaęž‰ handaęž‰pe leekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo tembolo da handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu handaataęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi la alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiao homenaęž‰ lie. Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao homenaęž‰ lie lemekeme. Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ipiki mea pua aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao lipe laa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ketete maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na handaęž‰ uaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 7 Mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ pi ulumaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Koto polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ dupiki hali homaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke halome leeke handa lomaęž‰me lemekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Pailedimaęž‰ koto lemeke pi opuaataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ wotu homaataęž‰  
\v 9 mo da tieke paęž‰taęž‰ paa hondaęž‰ pamba pua Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe leekepate pa ipikaęž‰ pi Yesumaęž‰ na yokaęž‰ mea haleekeme.  
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lelipiki laa neke da paa tapaowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ neke tamendiao linaęž‰ loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ hone na witele leekeme.  
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ oli manda halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ na kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yolo pime. Koto ekinaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hatuku mea epeaęž‰ hali ipikitaęž‰ ketete tieke paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Pailedimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ Yesu paa tapaalo pieke potaęž‰ weiyu taapeekepate mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi la alualu pea alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do hali paa tapaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ Sisanaęž‰ yankeke na halipikie laataęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone kini hali haluekemaęž‰ taapeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ Sisanaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki hali halieke lemekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Pailedimaęž‰ koto lemekeeki opuaataęž‰ Yesu hatuku hama peekeme. Kutupa pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ pitu hayeke seanaęž‰ pitiekeme. Koto sea wieke alenaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Toopi Yameekeekie. Koto bikitaęž‰ mo Hibulu pimaęž‰ Kaęž‰baęž‰ta lemekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Kutu pimiki ekitaęž‰ hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ekinaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ pimikime. Pailedimaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ kini hali kotomaęž‰ handaęž‰pe leekeme.  
\v 15 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi la alu alu pitolo alotaęž‰ Li li laa aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao lima lemekeme. Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ kini halitaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao IĚ±maęž‰ lionope leekeme. Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ kini halitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Sisa homekee lemekeme.  
\v 16 Koto lemeke handaa Pailedimaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ Yesu tamendiao linaęž‰yeke mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu haleekeme.  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ ta mea endiao homeekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰32-44, Maka 15ęž‰21-32, Luku 23ęž‰26-43)  
\p Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesu minimikime.  
\v 17 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki ti mea tia pua mo daoni hamaęž‰ nane hayeke alenaęž‰ opolo peekeme. Mo kenke bikitaęž‰ Hali you holikimaęž‰ handeke alenaęž‰ lo haemekeme. Hibulu pi laataęž‰ Kolokoda lemekeme.  
\v 18 Koto alenaęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ Yesu tamendiao lia aęž‰meiyao nokepemekeme. Hali yaapo make nepoko nane yaaponaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ mandane endiao maęž‰ndaęž‰ mandane endiao Yesu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ endiaotaęž‰ limikime.   
\p
\v 19 Pailedimaęž‰ pi siki wape pea mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ talaenaęž‰ leekeme. Koto wape pieke ekitaęž‰ dupae. Naęž‰saęž‰tete Hali Yesutaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie laa wape piekeme.  
\v 20 Mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ Yesu tamendiaemeke alenaęž‰ daoni teke paęž‰taęž‰ yolo hataęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ mo wape pieke ekitaęž‰ handemekeme. Mo wape pieke pitaęž‰ Hibulu pi make Lomaęž‰ pi make Kitiki pi make wape piekeme.  
\v 21 Mo yeni peao haemeke Diu you haliwekimaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie wape na piki Do halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie leekeme laa wape peaęž‰peke aleo lemekeme.  
\v 22 Pailedimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ wape polo ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ wape puaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 23 Mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ Yesu lu endiaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau manutaęž‰ mea iki tonkopu hali hataęž‰ telipea mimikime. Ipikaęž‰ dau hokulupeke lopaniaeyekeeki make mimikipate koto dautaęž‰ na tunaakeeki kone homeke kone tumbula lopaniaeyekeeki yeeke handaa  
\v 24 mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Na sinkipiki pa mo minaęž‰laęž‰ hali handomanaęž‰ laki pumanaęž‰e lemekeme. Hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki yaaluekemaęž‰ pimikime. Wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Yaka dau manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ telipa meaataęž‰ yaka hokulupeke dau muluekemaęž‰ laki pimikime laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\p Kotaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndeli miniki haliwekimaęž‰ kutu pimikime.   
\p
\v 25 Mo Yesu ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki ti teke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki make inkikinaęž‰ hakepiki make Keliopasinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Meti kutupa mo Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Meti make paeyao koto pambo haemekeme.  
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki make ipikaęž‰ hande pukimaęž‰ homeeke disaipolo hali make ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ haepekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ weki koto handaęž‰e laataęž‰  
\v 27 mo disaipolo hali paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ koto handaęž‰e laa leekeme. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo disaipolo halimaęž‰ Meti ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pua handeteke hao hayekeme.   
\s1 Yesu otaęž‰ homeekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰45-56, Maka 15ęž‰33-41, Luku 23ęž‰44-49)  
\p
\v 28 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ pu paeyaalome hone wiaataęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki yaaluekemaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± ikali naęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 29 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo pinika ikali tumba pitieke ikali kanake homeke wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰mbimaęž‰ handeke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea mo pinika ikali paęž‰taęž‰ tenke lao ti hotinaęž‰ hapu lao mea aęž‰meiyao Yesunaęž‰ hambiliki paęž‰taęž‰ hapulaemekeme.  
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ mo pinika ikali naa alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ paelaęž‰me leekeme. Koto laa ipikitaęž‰ you tokaęž‰laęž‰niao homeekeme.   
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰likinaęž‰ awo liekeeki  
\p
\v 31 Koto pimiki ekitaęž‰ hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ yeeke handaataęž‰ mo Diu haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Beliataęž‰ hande Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate otaęž‰ tieke konee hone witolo hataęž‰ mo hali tokomanu aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ na endi pelia haenaęž‰ hone wimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo hali teponaęž‰ ankemanu tondaęž‰paęž‰ lia ikaęž‰ tokomanu hondaęž‰ minaęž‰yeke honke lemekeme.  
\v 32 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ami haliwekimaęž‰ pua mo Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ limiki hali yaaponaęž‰ ankemanu tondaęž‰paęž‰ limikime.  
\v 33 Kutupa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pemekepate ipikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homa toko wiekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anke yaapo na tondaęž‰paęž‰ limikime.  
\v 34 Kutu pimikipate mo ami hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dolomaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰liki paęž‰taęž‰ awaęž‰liaeyekeme. Kutu pieke handaa kutaa kone we tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikali tonkaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰pa lopeekeme.  
\v 35 Kutu piaęž‰eki handeaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi opua miniki haminaęž‰yeke kone koto ambaęž‰ leaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki alome laa ipikaęž‰ kone hone witaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 36 Koto hau pieke ekimaęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki yaeyekeme. Mo wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Ipikaęž‰ hokaęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na tondaęž‰paęž‰ limikie wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 37 Kutupa mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupae. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo awemeke hali handilimikie wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Yesu toko toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰57-61, Maka 15ęž‰42-47, Luku 23ęž‰50-56)  
\p
\v 38 Koto hau pimikieki hoki nane mo Aęž‰taęž‰matia da hao epeeke hali Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu toko mea poluekemaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ pua honke leekeme. Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi opu hayekepate mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰ hataęž‰ puki toolumaęž‰ piekeme. Pailedimaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leeke handaa Diosepemaęž‰ pua mea peekeme.  
\v 39 Ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hande timba Yesu handolo peeke hali Nikodimasi make Diosepe yaapo puaataęž‰ totopo piki ale yaapo mua make aęž‰lo make mea dakole dakole peaeyekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mendia pepekeme. Mo senisi alenaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ 34 kiloe.  
\v 40 Mo hali yaapomaęž‰ Yesu toko hondaęž‰ meaataęž‰ hande totopo piki senisi alemanu mea yankaotaęž‰ daumaęž‰ ambulaęž‰niaepeke ekitaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hali hoiluekemaęž‰ toko wamo pu haemeke tupaęž‰ pipikime.  
\v 41 Mo Yesu aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ limiki alenaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ e pokemekeme. Koto e tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hali hoiyaęž‰peke ale panake wepia wiekeeki wiekeme. Ambaęž‰taęž‰ hali toko maęž‰ndaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ na wimikime.  
\v 42 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu toko mea pua wipiki ekitaęž‰ pa mo hali hoiyaęž‰peke lapaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yeke make mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate belia epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ peaęž‰peke ekimanu wamo puluekemaęž‰ nate yeke make pipikime.   
\c 20  
\s1 Yesu paa tiaeyekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰1-8, Maka 16ęž‰1-8, Luku 24ęž‰1-12)  
\p
\v 1 Da kelepuluekemaęž‰ yu paĚ±aĚ± pitolo haenaęž‰ Sande kone Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Metitaęž‰ hande hali hoimiki paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ hande naku kake aęž‰mbaniao wimiki toopitaęž‰ paa londolo wiekeeki handeekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa handa anke hao pua Saimono Pida paęž‰taęž‰ make hande Yesumaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeeke disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make ipiliki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Mo hande naku paęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali toko yoka wilimieki make na handolomaęž‰maęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ wia pelemepe leekeme.   
\p
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pidataęž‰ hande disaipolo hali yaapotaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo hali hoimiki paęž‰taęž‰ pepekeme.  
\v 4 Anke homeke halupa pepekepate hande disaipolo halitaęž‰ Pida wetepeao ipiki ambaęž‰la mo hali hoimiki paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ pua pandaęž‰puniao hande hali tonkao hoimiki daumanu wiekeeki handeekepate na hondaęž‰ pambolo peekeme.  
\v 6 Saimono Pidataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa kutaa kone lombei pua mo naku paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hande hali tonkao hoimiki daumanu make  
\v 7 Yesunaęž‰ you tonkaemeke dau make handeekeme. Koto dautaęž‰ hande hali tonkao hoimiki daumanu apaęž‰tao na wiki pa tonkaake tonkaęž‰naęž‰ pa ipikaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeme.  
\v 8 Pidamaęž‰ kutu pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ hande hali hoimiki paęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la peeke disaipolo hali make wetepenaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua mo piekeeki handaataęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulaeyekeme.  
\v 9 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ homaa paa tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰eki wape pieke ekitaęž‰ hone aĚ±iĚ± na wipikime.  
\v 10 Kutupataęž‰ mo disaipolo hali yaapotaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la da nane pepekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Meti Maęž‰kadala paęž‰taęž‰ pua hayekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰9-10, Maka 16ęž‰9-11)  
\p
\v 11 Metimaęž‰taęž‰ hande hali hoimiki paęž‰taęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane eĚ± lo hayekeme. EĚ± alo alo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao mo hali hoimiki paęž‰taęž‰ wako puniaeyekepate  
\v 12 koto paęž‰taęž‰ enisolo yaapo handeekeme. Mo hali yaapotaęž‰ hakepiki dau pamba alu pea Yesu toko ambaęž‰ wimiki alenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ you nane pitu maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ anke nane pitu pea pitipikime.  
\v 13 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ Meti paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Ekipeke eĚ± alepe lepekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka Tekehali mea pua wilimi paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ± na handolome leekeme.  
\v 14 Kotoeki laa laęž‰kaęž‰la koto paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hayekeeki handeekepate kone Yesue hone na wiekeme.  
\v 15 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰o. Ekipeke eĚ± alepe. Epi weitolo alepe leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ hone wieke ekitaęž‰ mo e handeteke hayeke hali patemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki mea pua wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wili alenaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kie. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mulu polueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 16 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Metio leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la mina hataęž‰ Hibulu pi la alotaęž‰ Labonaie leekeme. Koto leeke ekitaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio laa leekeme.  
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± na minaęž‰pe. Yaka Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰meilo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Yaka kametiti paęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi lawaalo puaęž‰peke. Yaka Apaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ make yaka Kodaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰meinolome lapeke leekeme.  
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰ Meti Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pua Tekehali handeekeeki make Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ leeke pimanu make la haleekeme.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pua hayekeeki  
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰16-20, Maka 16ęž‰14-18, Luku 24ęž‰36-49)  
\p
\v 19 Koto Sande timbaataęž‰ mo hande disaipolo ameĚ±leĚ± pomu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo Diu haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ da potaęž‰manu poka lokaęž‰ hao da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitimikipate Yesumaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ puki lopaęž‰niaape leekeme.  
\v 20 Koto laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapo make ipikaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰liki iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu handaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke homemekeme.  
\v 21 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ puki lopaęž‰niao hape laa Hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± epono tapaalaęž‰ tupaęž‰ iki make pominaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ tapaasome leekeme.  
\v 22 Kotoeki laataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pomo puaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hande Holi Sipitidi iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitolomaęž‰ mipe leekeme.  
\v 23 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa paeyaalaęž‰me lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa paeyaalieke. Kutupa make mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa na paeyaalaęž‰me laa lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ na paeyaake paa wilieke la leekeme.   
\s1 Yesu Tomasi yaapo  
\p
\v 24 Mo Yesu epeeke natenaęž‰ hande disaipolo hali homeke iki ameĚ±leĚ± na pitiekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Tomasi kone ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Mandaęž‰e.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehali handomaęž‰me lemekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ ikokomaęž‰ aweekeeki handaa yaka kiki maĚ±leke puaotaęž‰ kutupa ipikaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰likinaęž‰ aweekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ make yaka kiki puaotaęž‰ otaęž‰e lolo polopate IĚ±maęž‰ na handeke hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aleme pitaęž‰ na opulueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 26 Kutupa pula homeke paeyeketaęž‰ hande disaipolo haliweki Tomasi ameĚ±leĚ± mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa mombaęž‰la haemekeme. Mo potaęž‰manu lokaęž‰ hao haemekepate Yesu aęž‰paataęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ puki lopao pitaęž‰pe laataęž‰  
\v 27 Mo Tomasi paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kiki maĚ±lekemaęž‰ yaka kiki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa puae. Kutupa nakaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ ya paęž‰taęž‰liki paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰pa puae. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi na opitele hau paa na piki otaęž‰ opuaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 28 Tomasimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ yaka Tekehali make yaka Kodaęž‰ make haleme leekeme.  
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± handele ekimaęž‰ pi opitele laa IĚ± na handeke hataęž‰ kone pi mineleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa halimikie leekeme.   
\s1 Do buka wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi teke  
\p
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ mandane wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu wotu piekepate do bukanaęž‰ wape na paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 31 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Ketiso make Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke make halaęž‰me laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki muemenaęž‰yeke do ekimanu do bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰me.   
\c 21  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali watake hataęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua hayekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki peneme yao paa waleekeme. Mo tunkulaęž‰ pa pitieke ikali Taibitiasi paęž‰taęž‰ pua hataęž‰ dupa piekeme.  
\v 2 Saimono Pida make hande Mandaęž‰e lemeke hali Tomasi make hande Kaęž‰lili nane Keina da hao epeeke hali Nadaęž‰niele make Sepedi ipikaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo make Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ make paeyao mandake paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la haemekeme.  
\v 3 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ mo hande mandane haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Taęž‰peli mulu pulume leeke handaa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki make neke ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pomanaęž‰e lemekeme. Koto la pua kawasonaęž‰ pita pemekepate koto timbaataęž‰ taęž‰peli homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na mimikime.   
\p
\v 4 Nate panake opolo haenaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰pa hayekepate mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesue hone na wimikime.  
\v 5 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Weki tonuo. Taęž‰peli maęž‰ndaęž‰ mimipe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me lemekeme.  
\v 6 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kawasonaęž‰ popeke nane tenkinu mea lopaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰pelimanu milimikie leekeme. Koto leeke handaa mo haliwekimaęž‰ tenkinu mea lopaemekepate taęž‰pelimanu wotu mendieke handaa mo tenkinu paa yolaęž‰ miaęž‰peke na yeekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Hande Yesumaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeeke disaipolo hali homekemaęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Tekehalie leekeme. Saimono Pidamaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Tekehalie leekeeki opuataęž‰ ambaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau hola wieke handaa ipikaęž‰ manda tonkaeyekeeki paa mea tonkao ikali paęž‰taęž‰ ponkaeyekeme.  
\v 8 Mo hande mandane disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ kawasonaęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ mo tenkinu taęž‰peli manumaęž‰ tumba winaęž‰ yolo tia ikali teaęž‰ nane opolo epemekeme. Mo haliwekitaęž‰ ikali teaęž‰ nane opolo ipuluekemaęž‰ makataęž‰ 100 midamanu kone epemekeme.  
\v 9 Kenkenaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pataęž‰ ti to hayeke alenaęž‰ taęž‰peli palaowa yaapo to hayekeeki handemekeme.  
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ ame do mimi taęž‰peli mandaneeki mea ipupe leekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Saimono Pidamaęž‰ kawasonaęž‰ pua mo tenkinu kenkenaęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea epeekeme. Mo nu mendia tumbulu baeyeke taęž‰peli manutaęž‰ paeyao 153 mendiekeme. Taęž‰peli wopu mendiekepate kone mo tenkinutaęž‰ na titipilaęž‰niaeyekeme.  
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ne nolo ipupe leekepate mo disaipolo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Tekehalie hone wimiki handaa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Neketaęž‰ epikaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ na piekeme.  
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ palaowa mulu pua iki paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale pea taęž‰peli make koto tupaęž‰ kone haleekeme.   
\p
\v 14 Do hau pieke ekitaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ homa paa tiao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ hoto tepo peao ipiki peneme yao waleekeekie.   
\s1 Yesu Pida yaapo  
\p
\v 15 Ne no paeyeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Saimono Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ eiyeke Saimonoo. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ do haliweki ankulalipikipe leekeme. Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe Tekehalio. IĚ±maęž‰ neke hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handeleme leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ ya sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ ikikisunu nakanaęž‰maęž‰ punao hapeke leekeme.  
\v 16 Hoto yaapo peao Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ eiyeke Saimonoo. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelepe leeke handaa Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe Tekehalio. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ ya sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu nakanaęž‰maęž‰ punao hapeke leekeme.  
\v 17 Hoto tepo peao Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ eiyeke Saimonoo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.  
\p Pidamaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰pe pi ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hoto tepo peao lotaęž‰ pieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ punao hapeke.  
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Neke wekihali hae dinaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ baęž‰taęž‰ido hako yama nakaęž‰ hone piaęž‰ nane pomu hayekeme. Kutupu hayekepate wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ neke koke yolo paęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kiki yaapo tindipa moneaalo pelepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ kiki mea tonkao nakaęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰ nane kone neke hatuku pelieke leekeme.  
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ do leeke ekimaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homolo pieke ekinaęž‰ la hololo leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ kotoeki laa Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea epoe leekeme.   
\s1 Yesu make mo hande disaipolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ make  
\p
\v 20 Pidamaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰moneao Yesumaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeeke halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane epeekeeki handeekeme. Mo halitaęž‰ hande ne nalo pitaęž‰ Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Neke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombolo paęž‰laęž‰ hali epipe leeke halie.  
\v 21 Pidamaęž‰ koto hali handaa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki hau ipiliepe leekeme.  
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ pa hatiki puoopu hao IĚ± paa eponoyeke ya hone wia loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea epoe leekeme.  
\v 23 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliwekimaęž‰ dupiki pi lo haemekeme. Mo hande disaipolo halitaęž‰ na homilieke laa lo haemekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo hande hali na homilieke pi na leke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do halitaęž‰ pa hatiki puoopu hao IĚ± paa eponoyeke ya hone wia loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰eki diaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Mo hande disaipolo hali doe. Kutupa koto pieke ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ laa kutupa make wape piaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ ekie hone witolomaęž‰me.   
\s1 Paeyaasoeki  
\p
\v 25 Yesumaęž‰ hau mandane ekimanu wopu piekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu paeyao homeke homeke lo wape piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wape piaęž‰peke buka manumaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke tumbulu baaso anaęž‰ na pilieke hone witolome.   